Safety is also a top priority, with features like forward collision alert, lane keep assist, and a high-definition rear vision camera keeping you and your passengers secure on the road.

Experience the uncompromising capability and refined luxury of the 2019 GMC Sierra 1500 AT4. Visit our showroom today and let us demonstrate how this exceptional truck can elevate your driving experience.

description:
Discover the perfect blend of luxury and capability in this stunning 2021 Lexus RX 350 PREMIUM PACKAGE. This meticulously maintained SUV boasts a sleek black exterior and a wealth of premium features that elevate the driving experience.

• CLEAN CARFAX
• BLIND SPOT MONITOR
• PREMIUM PACKAGE
• AWD
• Premium Package
• 9 Speakers
• AM/FM radio: SiriusXM
• AM/FM/CD Radio
• CD player
• Radio data system
• Air Conditioning
• Automatic temperature control
• Front dual zone A/C
• Rear window defroster
• Power driver seat
• Power steering
• Power windows
• Remote keyless entry
• Steering wheel mounted audio controls
• Touch-Free Power Rear Door w/Kick Sensor

Powered by a robust 3.5L V6 DOHC 24V engine and equipped with an 8-Speed Automatic transmission, this Lexus RX 350 delivers impressive performance and efficiency, with an EPA-estimated 19 MPG in the city and 26 MPG on the highway. The all-wheel-drive system provides confident handling and traction, making it the perfect companion for all your adventures.

Step inside this well-appointed cabin and experience the true meaning of luxury. The Premium Package adds a wealth of premium amenities, including a Wood & Leather Heated Steering Wheel, Intuitive Parking Assist & Rr Cross Traffic Alert, Genuine wood console and door panel inserts, and Heated & Ventilated Front Seats. The NuLuxe Seat Trim and Power Passenger Seat ensure maximum comfort, while the Split Folding Rear Seat offers versatility to accommodate your cargo needs.

Safety is of the utmost importance, and this Lexus RX 350 is equipped with a comprehensive suite of advanced safety features, including Blind Spot Monitor, Rear Cross-Traffic Alert, and a Rear-View Camera. You can drive with confidence, knowing that you and your loved ones are well-protected.

Experience the exceptional craftsmanship, performance, and technology that make the 2021 Lexus RX 350 PREMIUM PACKAGE a true standout in the luxury SUV segment. Schedule a test drive today and discover the difference that Lexus quality can make in your driving experience.

Cruise control provides comfort on longer drives, and the spacious cabin layout is optimized for convenience and productivity. description: A Free CARFAX for this vehicle is available at schompbmw.com, where you can view the vehicle history report, ownership history, and maintenance reports.Introducing the BMW X3 M50, a luxurious and powerful vehicle designed to elevate your driving experience. This Sport Utility Vehicle (SUV)/Multi-Purpose Vehicle (MPV) embodies the perfect blend of style, performance, and cutting-edge technology.The BMW X3 M50 boasts a robust 3-liter 6-cylinder engine capable of delivering an impressive 393 horsepower, ensuring exhilarating acceleration and responsive handling. Safety features include standard ABS, Forward Collision Warning, and Airbags located in the 1st row for both driver and passenger, as well as 1st and 2nd-row Curtain Airbags for all-around protection.Its striking Alpine White exterior color beautifully complements the sleek design of the BMW X3 M50. The LED Lower Beam Headlamp Light Source not only enhances visibility but also adds a touch of modern elegance to the vehicle's appearance. The trim features Black Perforated and Qui upholstery, providing both comfort and sophistication for all occupants.Convenience and innovation are seamlessly integrated into this vehicle, with standard features such as Park Assist, Pedestrian Automatic Emergency Braking, and a Direct Tire Pressure Monitoring System (TPMS). The interior is designed for optimal comfort and practicality, featuring comfortable seating for multiple passengers along with Manual Seat Belts for added safety.With advanced technologies like Lane Departure Warning and optional Lane Centering Assistance, the BMW X3 M50 offers an enhanced driving experience that prioritizes safety and convenience. The seamless integration of these features reflects BMW's commitment to providing a premium driving experience.Whether you are cruising on city streets or embarking on a long journey, the BMW X3 M50 promises to deliver performance, comfort, and style in one exceptional package. Safety and Security
  • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
  • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
  • Pedestrian impact prevention - An extra step toward safety. Pedestrians don't always stop, look, and listen, but with Pedestrian Impact Prevention, your vehicle is equipped to better see them and avoid them. This system constantly monitors the road ahead to identify and track pedestrians. It projects that image to an interior display screen, AND should an impact become likely, Pedestrian impact prevention takes steps to avoid a collision.
Technology and Telematics
  • Apple CarPlay Compatibility smart device wireless mirroring
  • Mobile hotspot - WiFi on the fly. Connect your devices to the Internet through your vehicle's private mobile hotspot and take the internet wherever your journey takes you, without eating up your data allowance. Find the hotspot with mobile hotspot.

description:
Discover the epitome of family-friendly luxury with the 2026 Toyota Sienna Platinum 7 Passenger. This exceptional minivan seamlessly blends advanced technology, exceptional comfort, and uncompromising safety to create a truly remarkable driving experience.

Boasting a striking Red exterior, this Sienna Platinum is equipped with a robust 2.5L I4 engine and AWD, delivering an impressive 34 city/36 highway MPG. Elevate your commute with the following premium features:

• AWD
• Toyota Safety Sense
• Apple CarPlay
• Android Auto
• Sunroof/Moonroof
• Cooled Seats
• Heated Seats
• Keyless Access with Push Button Start

Indulge in the Platinum Package, which includes a premium navigation system, a 12-speaker JBL audio system, and a heads-up display to keep you informed and entertained. The power liftgate and panoramic moonroof add a touch of elegance and convenience, while the leather-trimmed, heated, and ventilated seats ensure unparalleled comfort for all passengers.

Safety is paramount in the 2026 Sienna Platinum. Equipped with a comprehensive suite of advanced safety technologies, including lane departure warning, automatic high beams, and a rear-view camera, you can navigate the roads with confidence. The emergency communication system and airbag protection provide additional peace of mind for you and your loved ones.

Versatility is at the heart of the Sienna Platinum. The split-folding third-row seats and power-adjustable driver's seat with memory function allow you to easily accommodate passengers and cargo, while the rear air conditioning and heated rear seats ensure everyone travels in comfort.

Experience the pinnacle of family-focused luxury with the 2026 Toyota Sienna Platinum 7 Passenger. Visit our showroom today to take this exceptional minivan for a test drive and discover how it can elevate your driving experience.

  • The driver can remotely control the parking procedure from outside the vehicle.
  • If the vehicle detects prolonged driver unresponsiveness it will automatically bring the vehicle to a stop and turn on the hazard lights. If equipped, emergency services will be contacted.
Safety and Security
  • The vehicle is equipped with a system that senses, and then prepares, the vehicle and/or occupants, for an impending forward collision.
  • The vehicle constantly monitors the roadway in front of the vehicle and identifies and tracks pedestrians on an interior display. If the system determines a likely impact, it will automatically take preventative steps to avoid hitting the pedestrian.
  • The vehicle is equipped with a camera that displays an image of the area behind the vehicle on an interior display.
Technology and Telematics
  • Wireless App-Connect (w/Apple CarPlay, Android Auto & MirrorLink) smart device wireless mirroring
  • Mobile devices can wirelessly connect to the internet through the vehicle's private mobile network.

description: [NEW] CHASSIS (Chrysler Voyager) & [NEW] BraunAbility (Manual-Companion) ConversionThe BraunAbility conversions on the Chrysler Pacifica and Chrysler Voyager offer unmatched versatility, spacious design, and industry leading accessibility. These wheelchair accessible minivans are available in both side-entry and rear-entry models, with your choice of fold-out or in-floor ramp systems, along with multiple floor height options. Whether you're a driver or passenger, BraunAbility delivers flexible solutions to meet your mobility needs.Known for their generous interior space, the Pacifica and Voyager conversions provide one of the most comfortable and user-friendly experiences available. From easy entries and exits to superior in-cabin maneuverability, BraunAbility offers a lineup that adapts to your lifestyle and budget.With more configuration options than any other mobility van manufacturer, BraunAbility allows you to select the vehicle that fits you best, whether it's a side-entry or rear-entry model, and whether you need a fold-out ramp or prefer an in-floor design for a clean, uncluttered cabin.*Key Benefits of BraunAbility Chrysler Pacifica and Voyager Conversions:* * Most spacious wheelchair accessible interior in the industry * Tallest and widest doorway openings for ease of access * Available in both side-entry and rear-entry configurations * Choice of fold-out or in-floor ramp systems * Multiple floor height options to accommodate a range of mobility devices*Ramp System Features:* * Widest side-entry ramp available in the industry * Heavy duty ramp with a 1,000 lb. weight capacity for long lasting strength and stability * Smooth ramp operation designed for durability and safety*Convenience and Comfort:* * Soft glow interior lighting for safe nighttime navigation * External lighting for ramp visibility in low light conditions * Remote access via integrated key fob * Thoughtful interior features, including easily accessible cupholders and storage spaces * Functional, driver and passenger friendly layout designed for everyday useWhether you're looking for a vehicle that provides freedom, comfort, or peace of mind, the BraunAbility Chrysler Pacifica or Voyager offers an excellent balance of quality engineering and accessible design. Contact us today to learn more about available configurations, pricing, and to schedule a test drive or demonstration.

description: Experience the Future of Family Travel with the 2025 Toyota Sienna Platinum: Where Comfort Meets Cutting-Edge Technology in a Hybrid Masterpiece Step into the 2025 Toyota Sienna Platinum, a used vehicle that redefines what it means to travel in style and efficiency. This Magnetic Gray Metallic beauty is not just a minivan it s a sanctuary on wheels, perfect for families who demand more from their drive. The 2.5L I4 Hybrid engine ensures eco-friendly journeys without compromising on power. Inside, you ll find a luxurious cabin adorned with leather seats, offering both heated and cooled options for front passengers, ensuring comfort in any climate. The third-row seating and rear bucket seats provide ample space for everyone, making long trips a breeze. Safety is paramount, with features like a Blind Spot Monitor, Lane Departure Warning, and Front Collision Mitigation, offering peace of mind on every journey. The advanced Adaptive Cruise Control and Lane Keeping Assist make highway driving effortless. Enjoy seamless connectivity with a premium sound system, Bluetooth, and a WiFi hotspot, keeping everyone entertained and connected. The hands-free liftgate and smart device integration add a touch of modern convenience, while the sun/moonroof invites the outside world in. The 2025 Toyota Sienna Platinum is not just a vehicle it s a lifestyle choice for those who value innovation, safety, and luxury.

Since 1972 Wiesner has been a name people around Houston and Conroe have trusted for great sales and service. Past Chairman of the Board and CEO John Wiesner was born in Richmond, Texas and grew up in Hempstead. He married Beth Sorsby, also of Hempstead. They were graduates of Southern Methodist University. Mr. Wiesner started his automotive career in Hempstead in 1949, then moved to Baytown. In 1977, he purchased the Buick-Pontiac-GMC dealership in Conroe which is now the main headquarters for the Wiesner Automotive Group. Today the Wiesner Family carries on the tradition started by their father and grand-father by maintaining that great level of trust through community involvement, promoting quality brands and standing behind the motto "Buy for Less at Wiesner".

description:
Experience the pinnacle of family transportation with the 2025 Kia Carnival MPV SX Prestige, available from Mission Viejo Kia - your Kia Platinum Dealer Award winner committed to delivering exceptional customer experiences. This stunning Panthera Metal masterpiece redefines what a modern family vehicle can be, combining luxury, versatility, and innovation in one impressive package.

According to CARFAX, this vehicle comes with a clean history report showing no accidents or damage reported since new. The CARFAX report verifies the mileage accuracy, giving you complete confidence in this vehicle's documented past. Better yet, you'll have additional peace of mind knowing this vehicle is still covered under its active manufacturer warranty, making it a smart and secure choice for your next vehicle.

Step into a world where every journey becomes a first-class experience. The Navy/Gray interior creates a sophisticated atmosphere, while the dual moonroof bathes the cabin in natural light, making even routine trips feel special. Whether you're carpooling to soccer practice or embarking on a cross-country adventure, the heated and cooled front seats ensure year-round comfort, while the premium sound system turns every drive into an immersive audio experience.

Family movie night takes on a whole new meaning with the rear seat entertainment package. Watch your children's faces light up as their favorite content comes to life on the road. The power sliding doors and smart power liftgate make loading everything from groceries to sports equipment a breeze, while the hands-free operation means you'll never have to fumble for keys with full arms again.

Technology seamlessly integrates into every aspect of the Carnival, with Android Auto and Apple CarPlay keeping you connected on the go. The navigation system with its heads-up display helps you arrive at your destination safely and efficiently, while the aerial view display system makes parking in tight spaces a stress-free experience. The WiFi hotspot ensures everyone stays connected, whether for homework or entertainment.

Safety comes standard with an impressive suite of advanced features. From front collision mitigation to lane keeping assist, blind spot monitoring to the comprehensive airbag system, every drive is wrapped in layers of protection. The automatic high beams and LED headlights illuminate your path clearly, while rain-sensing wipers automatically adjust to changing weather conditions.

The multi-zone climate control ensures everyone travels in their perfect temperature zone, while the leather seats with memory function remember your ideal position. The power-adjustable driver's seat with lumbar support makes long drives comfortable, and the premium sound system transforms your favorite playlist into a concert-like experience.

Ready to make this vehicle yours? Visit us at Mission Viejo Kia, located at 28802 Marguerite Pkwy, Mission Viejo, CA 92692. Give us a call at 949-347-0500 or explore our inventory online at https://www.missionviejokia.com/. We're here to help you find your perfect ride!

description:
Discover the epitome of modern family luxury with the 2025 Toyota Sienna Platinum 7 Passenger. This exceptional minivan seamlessly blends cutting-edge technology, unparalleled comfort, and a commanding presence that will captivate your senses.

Boasting a meticulously curated array of premium features, this Sienna is a true standout. Key highlights include:

• Navigation System
• Platinum Package
• 12 Speakers
• JBL Audio with Navigation
• Heads-Up Display
• Memory Seat
• Power Moonroof
• Rear-Seat Entertainment
• Power Liftgate
• Lane Departure Warning System

Step inside and be enveloped in a cabin that exudes sophistication and attention to detail. Sink into the plush, heated and ventilated leather seats, where every journey is a serene and indulgent experience. The Sienna's expansive interior provides ample room for up to seven passengers, ensuring everyone travels in uncompromised comfort.

Under the hood, the 2.5L I4 Hybrid engine with VVT-iE DOHC 16V delivers a remarkable balance of power and efficiency, offering an impressive 36 MPG in the city and on the highway. This advanced powertrain seamlessly blends electric and gasoline propulsion, providing a smooth, responsive, and remarkably eco-friendly driving experience.

The Sienna's advanced safety features, including the Lane Departure Warning System and Automatic High Beams, work tirelessly to keep you and your loved ones secure on the road. With a suite of airbags, electronic stability control, and a rear-view camera, you can navigate with confidence, knowing your family is protected.

Elevate your driving experience with the 2025 Toyota Sienna Platinum 7 Passenger. This exceptional minivan is the perfect fusion of style, technology, and uncompromising capability – a true masterpiece that will redefine your expectations of what a family vehicle can be.

We invite you to visit our showroom and explore this remarkable Sienna firsthand. Experience the difference for yourself and discover why it's the ultimate choice for discerning families. Let us help you unlock the full potential of this exceptional vehicle and embark on a journey of unparalleled luxury and convenience.

description:
Thank you for choosing Jack Burford Chevrolet. We hope this vehicle will be a welcomed addition to your family/business. If you have any questions about this, or any other vehicle that we have at our dealership please give us a call at (859) 623-3350. Please come us at Jack Burford Chevrolet. We are located at 819 on the Eastern By-Pass in Richmond, Ky. Platinum Package
    Safety and Security
    • Lane departure prevention - Keep it between the lines. It only takes a moment of inattention for your vehicle to drift. With lane departure prevention, your vehicle takes corrective action to help you avoid unintentionally moving out of your lane. Lane departure prevention is an extra level of safety for you and those around you.
    • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
    • Pedestrian impact prevention - An extra step toward safety. Pedestrians don't always stop, look, and listen, but with Pedestrian Impact Prevention, your vehicle is equipped to better see them and avoid them. This system constantly monitors the road ahead to identify and track pedestrians. It projects that image to an interior display screen, AND should an impact become likely, Pedestrian impact prevention takes steps to avoid a collision.
    • Hands-on cruise control. Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful. Cruise control only managed speed, but not distance or safety. Now, with hands-on cruise control, simply set your desired speed and let sensor technology maintain a safe distance between you and surrounding vehicles. It slows you down, speeds you up and even keeps you in your own lane. Meet your ultimate co-pilot with hands-on cruise control.
    Technology and Telematics
    • Smart device mirroring - Smartphone, meet smart car. You can control your device through your vehicle's infotainment system. Smart device mirroring brings together safety and convenience by making it easier to find what you're looking for while keeping your eyes on the road.
    Call Jack Burford Chevrolet, Inc. at 859-623-3350 to schedule your VIP test drive! Thank you for visiting www.jackburford.com, proudly serving Richmond, Lexington, Winchester, Berea, and all of Kentucky and beyond since 1964! *All prices plus, tax, lic, and dealer doc fee.

If youre looking for a dependable, comfortable, and well-equipped minivan thats been properly cared for, this Sienna XLE is an outstanding choice.

We do not participate in the high pressure tactics that most of the larger dealerships employ - no price gouging on warranties, insurances and other additional products (where the large dealers make a lot of money at your expense) and no bouncing from salesman to manager and back pressuring you to buy. We believe if you want the vehicle we have to offer, you will want to buy it - no pressure needed. We are here to assist you. Our vehicles are priced based on condition, mileage, and demand. All the vehicles we offer for sale are priced to sell and offer exceptional value for money - our goal is NOT to have simply the LOWEST PRICE but to offer the best value. Please do not confuse low prices with value - if something is "cheap" there is normally a reason and no two used cars are the same - so please call to discuss or test drive any of our vehicles with the understanding that we may not have the lowest price but our goal is to offer the best value for the price. We welcome any trade-ins and promise an honest and fair offer.

description: . Anything but dull, our 2021 Toyota Sienna LE AWD Minivan is here to take on today with style, technology, and an expressive Super White design! Powered by a 2.5 Liter 4 Cylinder and 3 Electric Motors generating a combined 245hp paired to an electronically controlled CVT for efficient passing, towing, and cruising. This sure-footed All Wheel Drive minivan also takes your family farther by returning nearly 36mpg on the highway, and it has a striking look you need to see for yourself. Be sure to check out the bold lines, LED lighting, rear spoiler, and alloy wheels, and try out the dual power-sliding side door for smart convenience. Our LE cabin is a great fit for your family with eight comfortable heated fabric front seats, eight-way power for the driver, a multifunction heated steering wheel, tri-zone automatic climate control, keyless entry, and top-notch connectivity. Stay ahead of your busy schedule by taking advantage of a 9-inch touchscreen, Apple CarPlay®, Android Auto®, WiFi/Amazon Alexa compatibility, Bluetooth®, and a six-speaker sound system, all complemented by impressive cargo space! Toyota keeps your whole crew out of harm's way with a backup camera, blind-spot monitor, and Safety Sense features, including adaptive cruise control, lane-keeping assistance, automatic braking, and more. Our Sienna LE is engineered for families on the go just like yours! Save this Page and Call for Availability. We Know You Will Enjoy Your Test Drive Towards Ownership!. 2021 Toyota Sienna XSE FWD — premium hybrid minivan with style, efficiency, and advanced tech, located in Louisville, KY. One Owner! OTHER NOTABLE FEATURES AND OPTIONS YOU SHOULD KNOW ABOUT: Safety and Security
  • Lane departure prevention - Keep it between the lines. It only takes a moment of inattention for your vehicle to drift. With lane departure prevention, your vehicle takes corrective action to help you avoid unintentionally moving out of your lane. Lane departure prevention is an extra level of safety for you and those around you.
  • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
  • Pedestrian impact prevention - An extra step toward safety. Pedestrians don't always stop, look, and listen, but with Pedestrian Impact Prevention, your vehicle is equipped to better see them and avoid them. This system constantly monitors the road ahead to identify and track pedestrians. It projects that image to an interior display screen, AND should an impact become likely, Pedestrian impact prevention takes steps to avoid a collision.
  • Hands-on cruise control. Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful. Cruise control only managed speed, but not distance or safety. Now, with hands-on cruise control, simply set your desired speed and let sensor technology maintain a safe distance between you and surrounding vehicles. It slows you down, speeds you up and even keeps you in your own lane. Meet your ultimate co-pilot with hands-on cruise control.
Technology and Telematics
  • Smart device mirroring - Smartphone, meet smart car. You can control your device through your vehicle's infotainment system. Smart device mirroring brings together safety and convenience by making it easier to find what you're looking for while keeping your eyes on the road.

description: Just arrived is this well-reviewed, FACTORY FRESH, NO-ACCIDENT, ONE-OWNER, OFF-LEASE, NONSMOKER, SEVEN-SEATING 2021 Toyota Sienna XLE! This uncompromising van is perfect for active weekend adventures and busy families alike. It boasts striking design cues, roomy seating, lots of safety features, and excellent fuel economy! The 2021 Toyota Sienna received the ''Family Green Car of the Year'' award from Green Car Journal, and also earned accolades for its safety and resale value, including a TOP SAFETY PICK+ from the Insurance Institute for Highway Safety (IIHS) and a Kelley Blue Book ''Best Minivan Resale Value'' award. The IIHS uses a different scale for grading collision avoidance features. The 2021 Sienna received the highest rating of Superior for its standard vehicle-to-vehicle front crash prevention system. With its odometer now hovering around the 35,209 mark, the engine, transmission and drive axles are STILL COVERED under the balance of the factory powertrain warranty until April 2026 or 60,000 miles (whichever occurs first)! Want to extend its warranty coverage? In most cases, we can provide expanded options to cover each vehicle with a valuable, comprehensive warranty for years to come! Yes, the 2021 Toyota Sienna is exclusively a hybrid, marking a complete redesign where all models come standard with a gasoline-electric hybrid powertrain, delivering excellent fuel economy. The Edmunds-recommended XLE trim adds: Keyless entry with push-button start Four-zone automatic climate control Power-adjustable passenger seat Sunroof Eight-speaker audio system Auto-dimming rearview mirror Simulated leather upholstery Heated front seats Leather-wrapped steering wheel 120-volt household-style power outlet ...and perhaps even more! You can view vehicle files above this description [on our site], which may include the original brochure and window sticker! WHY buy new when we have this absolutely LIKE-NEW 2021 Toyota Sienna available for THOUSANDS LESS than the price of a brand new one?! We will happily size up TRADE-IN OFFERS and have EXCELLENT FINANCE OPTIONS as well, so please give us a call at 732-919-0707 (Wall Township) or 856-881-2869 (Sewell) TODAY!

description:
Step into a realm where sophistication meets practicality with the 2021 Toyota Sienna XSE, a sleek masterpiece in Super White that commands attention on every journey. Its CVT transmission paired with a powerful 4-cylinder engine ensures an exhilarating drive, effortlessly powered through any terrain by its All-Wheel Drive system. Inside, the chic Grey Flannel interior offers a sanctuary of comfort and style, making every adventure unforgettable. CarFax No Accidents! CarFax One Owner! Popular Options and Features Include: Safety and Security
  • Lane departure prevention - Keep it between the lines. It only takes a moment of inattention for your vehicle to drift. With lane departure prevention, your vehicle takes corrective action to help you avoid unintentionally moving out of your lane. Lane departure prevention is an extra level of safety for you and those around you.
  • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
  • Pedestrian impact prevention - An extra step toward safety. Pedestrians don't always stop, look, and listen, but with Pedestrian Impact Prevention, your vehicle is equipped to better see them and avoid them. This system constantly monitors the road ahead to identify and track pedestrians. It projects that image to an interior display screen, AND should an impact become likely, Pedestrian impact prevention takes steps to avoid a collision.
  • Hands-on cruise control. Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful. Cruise control only managed speed, but not distance or safety. Now, with hands-on cruise control, simply set your desired speed and let sensor technology maintain a safe distance between you and surrounding vehicles. It slows you down, speeds you up and even keeps you in your own lane. Meet your ultimate co-pilot with hands-on cruise control.
Technology and Telematics
  • Smart device mirroring - Smartphone, meet smart car. You can control your device through your vehicle's infotainment system. Smart device mirroring brings together safety and convenience by making it easier to find what you're looking for while keeping your eyes on the road.
About Dublin Honda Not only are we Honda enthusiasts at Dublin Honda, we're dedicated members of the local community. Ken Harvey opened Dublin Honda in 1977 and has helped literally thousands upon thousands of Happy Honda Owners find and maintain their Hondas. To this day, Dublin Honda remains a family-owned and family-operated dealership, committed to the local community we serve and in which we live.

description:
Certified 2021 Toyota Sienna Platinum AWD - Premium Family Transportation
Experience luxury and versatility in this Celestial Silver Metallic 2021 Toyota Sienna Platinum with all-wheel drive. This Toyota Silver Certified minivan combines sophisticated style with practical functionality, perfect for families who refuse to compromise.
Key Highlights:

CarFax One Owner vehicle
Toyota Silver Certified with 136-point inspection
7-passenger seating configuration
Efficient 2.5L I4 engine delivering 35/36 MPG City/Highway
All-wheel drive capability for year-round confidence

Premium Comfort Features:
The Platinum Package delivers first-class comfort with heated and ventilated front bucket seats, heated second-row seats, and heated rear seats. The 3-spoke leather-wrapped heated steering wheel includes memory settings, while dual-zone climate control in both front and rear ensures everyone travels in comfort. Enjoy the expansive power moonroof and the convenience of a power liftgate.
Advanced Technology:
Stay connected and entertained with the premium JBL 12-speaker audio system, Apple CarPlay/Android Auto integration, and SiriusXM radio. The navigation system and head-up display keep you informed, while the wide-angle backup monitor and parking camera simplify maneuvering.
Safety and Convenience:
Drive with confidence using active cruise control, lane departure warning, auto high-beam headlights, and electronic stability control. Rain-sensing wipers, auto-dimming mirrors, and remote keyless entry with illuminated entry add everyday convenience.
Certified Peace of Mind:
This Toyota Silver Certified vehicle includes a 12-month/12,000-mile limited powertrain warranty, 24-hour roadside assistance, and warranty coverage honored at over 1,400 Toyota dealers across the continental U.S. and Canada. The transferable warranty adds significant resale value.
Visit Rhinelander Auto Group or call 715-365-8100 to schedule your test drive with one of our non-commission based sales consultants. We handle all DMV paperwork and accept trade-ins for a hassle-free experience.

This clean and versatile vehicle was recently acquired to our store here in St. Louis!

The Toyota Sienna LE focuses on space, comfort, and family utility. The Ash interior and 7-passenger layout make daily use simple and practical.

Key Features

- 2.5L 4-Cylinder Hybrid System with 245 combined net horsepower and ECVT

- Front-Wheel Drive

- 7-passenger seating with second-row bench and stowable center seat

- Dual power sliding side doors

- Configurable second row, 60/40 split and stowable third row with one-motion stow

- 9-inch touchscreen with Apple CarPlay and Android Auto, SiriusXM trial, and 6 USB charge ports

- Three-zone automatic climate control with rear cabin controls and power driver seat

- Toyota Safety Sense 2.0 with Pre-Collision System, Dynamic Radar Cruise Control, Lane Departure Alert with Steering Assist, Lane Tracing Assist, Blind Spot Monitor with Rear Cross-Traffic Alert

- LED headlights, push-button start, remote keyless entry

We just completed our Victory 182-point inspection, performed a maintenance inspection and battery test, topped off all fluids, and finished a full interior and exterior detail. Two keys included.

Recent service records show the vehicle was inspected, serviced, and reconditioned to meet Victory Pre-Owned standards.

This beauty has had and passed an extensive Victory 182-point inspection conducted by our factory-certified technicians.

Buy with confidence. Every Victory Pre-Owned vehicle includes a 90-day or 3,000-mile comprehensive warranty on top of any remaining factory coverage. Includes Car Doc Smart Connect to monitor fuel level, battery status, location, recalls, and maintenance scheduling right from your phone.

Ownership includes our Car Doc maintenance plan with 6 complimentary oil changes and 6 complimentary tire rotations during the first two years. Upgrade to a 3-year or 5-year Car Doc plan for added perks.

We are in the business of building relationships, not just selling vehicles.

Whether you have good credit, bad credit, or no credit, get pre-approved today:
https://www.victorytoyotastl.com/finance/get-pre-approved/

This vehicle WONT last long at this price!
We are a large used car superstore serving St. Louis, Kirkwood, Chesterfield, Ballwin, Fenton, and surrounding Missouri communities.

Call us NOW at (314) 849 3700

Please chat, email, text, or call to verify any information and to schedule your product preview.

Pricamo Bosanski/Hablamos Espanol

description:
Discover the perfect balance of style, comfort, and capability in the 2023 Honda Odyssey EX-L. This exceptional minivan is a true family-friendly powerhouse, designed to elevate your daily adventures and provide unparalleled convenience.

• Automatic temperature control
• Rear air conditioning
• Memory seat
• Power driver seat
• Steering wheel mounted audio controls
• A/V remote: CabinControl
• Four wheel independent suspension
• Power moonroof
• Power Liftgate
• Blind Spot Information (BSI) System warning
• Lane departure: Lane Keeping Assist System (LKAS) active
• Exterior Parking Camera Rear
• Auto High-beam Headlights
• Fully automatic headlights
• Adaptive Cruise Control: Adaptive Cruise Control (ACC) with Low-Speed Follow
• Heated door mirrors
• Apple CarPlay/Android Auto
• Auto-dimming Rear-View mirror
• Garage door transmitter: HomeLink

Boasting a powerful 3.5L V6 engine and a smooth 10-speed automatic transmission, this Odyssey EX-L delivers an exceptional blend of performance and efficiency, with an EPA-estimated 19 city/28 highway MPG. The spacious and versatile interior offers seating for up to eight, along with a wealth of premium features that elevate the driving experience.

Indulge in the comfort of leather-trimmed heated front seats, a power driver's seat with memory function, and a power liftgate for effortless loading and unloading. The Odyssey's advanced safety suite, including the Blind Spot Information System and Lane Keeping Assist, provides added peace of mind on the road.

Connectivity is seamless with Apple CarPlay and Android Auto integration, allowing you to stay connected and entertained. The Odyssey's impressive list of premium amenities, from the power moonroof to the HomeLink garage door transmitter, elevates the everyday to the extraordinary.

Experience the perfect blend of style, function, and technology in the 2023 Honda Odyssey EX-L. Visit our showroom today and discover how this exceptional minivan can transform your family's driving experience.

description:
Discover the ultimate family-friendly companion in the 2023 Honda Odyssey Touring. This exceptional minivan blends unparalleled versatility, advanced technology, and refined style, making it the perfect choice for your next adventure.

This 2023 Honda Odyssey Touring includes a Navigation system: Honda Satellite-Linked Navigation System.

• Navigation system: Honda Satellite-Linked Navigation System
• 7 Speakers
• AM/FM radio: SiriusXM
• CD player
• DVD-Audio
• Radio data system
• Radio: 160-Watt AM/FM/HD/SiriusXM Audio System
• Rear audio controls
• Air Conditioning
• Automatic temperature control
• Front dual zone A/C
• Rear air conditioning
• Rear window defroster
• Memory seat
• Power driver seat

Powered by a robust 3.5L V6 SOHC i-VTEC 24V engine and paired with a smooth-shifting 10-Speed Automatic transmission, the Odyssey Touring delivers an impressive balance of power and efficiency, achieving an EPA-estimated 19 MPG in the city and 28 MPG on the highway.

Beyond its impressive performance, the Odyssey Touring is equipped with a wealth of advanced features designed to enhance your driving experience. The spacious and versatile interior offers seating for up to eight passengers, with ample cargo space for all your family's needs. The power liftgate and blind spot monitoring system provide added convenience and peace of mind, while the panoramic moonroof and premium audio system create a truly immersive driving environment.

Safety is also a top priority in the Odyssey Touring, with a suite of advanced driver-assistance technologies, including Adaptive Cruise Control, Lane Keeping Assist, and Collision Mitigation Braking System. These cutting-edge features work together to help keep you and your loved ones protected on the road.

Whether you're embarking on a family road trip, shuttling the kids to their activities, or simply enjoying the daily commute, the 2023 Honda Odyssey Touring is the ultimate companion. Experience the perfect blend of functionality, technology, and style – visit our showroom today and discover the difference for yourself.

(Valid on vehicles under 90,000 miles and less than 7 years old). Discover comfort and versatility in this white 2023 Honda Odyssey EX-L! With its spacious 8-passenger leather-trimmed interior, heated front seats, and power-operated moonroof, every drive is a pleasure. Advanced safety features include Front Automatic Emergency Braking, Lane Keeping Assist, Adaptive Cruise Control, Blind Spot Monitoring, and Rear Cross Traffic Alert, giving you peace of mind for the whole family. Stay connected with Apple CarPlay, Android Auto, Bluetooth, and the HondaLink smart device app, all accessible on the 8-inch touchscreen. Enjoy hands-free convenience with a power liftgate, dual power sliding side doors, and remote engine start. The Odyssey's flexible cabin offers flat-folding third-row seating, tri-zone automatic climate control, and plenty of storage options for every adventure. Experience the smooth power of a 3.5L V6 engine with a 10-speed automatic transmission and enjoy features like auto-dimming rearview mirror, rearview camera, and premium audio with SiriusXM. Discover the perfect blend of style, comfort, and convenience in the 2023 Toyota Sienna XLE. This exceptional minivan is more than just a practical family hauler - it's a testament to Toyota's commitment to excellence.

Gray Leather interior.

• LIFETIME OIL CHANGES
• Carfax Accident Free
• Florida Driven

• Front and Rear Dual-Zone Climate Control

• Power Moonroof
• Power Liftgate
• Apple CarPlay and Android Auto Integration
• Auto-Dimming Rearview Mirror

Safety is paramount in the Sienna XLE, with features like Lane Departure Warning, Automatic High Beams, and a Rear-View Camera ensuring you and your loved ones arrive at your destination with confidence.

Whether you're embarking on a long road trip or navigating the daily school run, the 2023 Toyota Sienna XLE is the perfect companion. Its blend of style, technology, and practicality make it a standout choice in the minivan segment.

This 2023 Ford Transit Connect XL is a versatile and efficient commercial vehicle that's perfect for your business needs. With its spacious interior, advanced technology features, and impressive fuel economy, this Transit Connect is the ideal choice for entrepreneurs and small business owners.

Powered by a reliable 2.0L I4 engine and equipped with an 8-speed automatic transmission, this Transit Connect delivers a smooth and responsive driving experience. The front-wheel-drive configuration ensures confident handling, even in challenging conditions. And with an EPA-estimated 24 city/26 highway MPG, you'll spend less time and money at the pump, allowing you to focus on what really matters – growing your business.

The exterior of this Transit Connect is clean and modern, with a sleek white paint finish that conveys a professional appearance. The 16-inch steel wheels and body-color bumpers add a touch of ruggedness, while the rear parking sensors and backup camera make maneuvering in tight spaces a breeze.

Step inside, and you'll be greeted by a well-appointed interior that prioritizes functionality and comfort. The vinyl front bucket seats provide all-day support, while the tilt and telescoping steering wheel allows you to find the perfect driving position. The AM/FM radio with Bluetooth connectivity keeps you connected on the go, and the dual-zone climate control ensures a comfortable cabin environment for you and your passengers.

But the real standout features of this Transit Connect are its impressive cargo capabilities. With a maximum payload of over 1,600 pounds and a generous 122.3 cubic feet of cargo volume, this van can handle all your business needs, from transporting equipment to delivering supplies. The rear liftgate and sliding side doors make loading and unloading a breeze, and the available roof rack system provides additional storage options.

Whether you're a contractor, a delivery service, or a small business owner, this 2023 Ford Transit Connect XL is the perfect companion for your commercial endeavors. With its combination of functionality, efficiency, and technology, this van is sure to exceed your expectations and help you take your business to new heights.

This Certified 2023 Honda Odyssey Touring, has a Obsidian Blue Pearl exterior and an Gray interior color. 57,276 miles. Stock Number 18559PV. You can connect with us by calling (866) 471-9998. No Accidents! One Owner! Important Package and Feature Information Safety and Security
  • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
  • Pedestrian impact prevention - An extra step toward safety. Pedestrians don't always stop, look, and listen, but with Pedestrian Impact Prevention, your vehicle is equipped to better see them and avoid them. This system constantly monitors the road ahead to identify and track pedestrians. It projects that image to an interior display screen, AND should an impact become likely, Pedestrian impact prevention takes steps to avoid a collision.
  • Rear camera - Watching your back! The rear camera helps you see obstacles and hazards you otherwise couldn't by showing enhanced images of what is behind you. The rear camera is an extra set of eyes that's both convenient and safe.
Technology and Telematics
  • Smart device mirroring - Smartphone, meet smart car. You can control your device through your vehicle's infotainment system. Smart device mirroring brings together safety and convenience by making it easier to find what you're looking for while keeping your eyes on the road.
  • Mobile hotspot - WiFi on the fly. Connect your devices to the Internet through your vehicle's private mobile hotspot and take the internet wherever your journey takes you, without eating up your data allowance. Find the hotspot with mobile hotspot.

description:
Discover the exceptional 2023 Honda Odyssey EX-L, a family-focused masterpiece that blends unparalleled versatility, cutting-edge technology, and refined style. This captivating minivan is poised to elevate your daily driving experience, offering a seamless blend of practicality and sophistication.

Boasting a stunning White exterior, the Odyssey EX-L commands attention with its sleek lines and modern aesthetic. Powered by a robust 3.5L V6 SOHC i-VTEC 24V engine paired with a smooth 10-Speed Automatic transmission, this FWD marvel delivers an impressive balance of performance and efficiency, with an EPA-estimated 19 city/28 highway MPG.

• Handsfree Bluetooth
• USB Port
• 7 Speakers
• AM/FM radio: SiriusXM
• Automatic temperature control
• Power driver seat
• Power moonroof
• Power Liftgate
• Blind Spot Information (BSI) System warning
• Adaptive Cruise Control: Adaptive Cruise Control (ACC) with Low-Speed Follow
• Apple CarPlay/Android Auto
• Leather Seat Trim
• Heated Front Bucket Seats
• 18" Machine-Finished Alloy Wheels

Step inside the Odyssey EX-L and experience the epitome of family-friendly luxury. The spacious and thoughtfully designed cabin offers seating for up to 8 passengers, with ample room for everyone and their gear. The leather-trimmed seats provide exceptional comfort, while the heated front buckets ensure a cozy ride on even the chilliest days.

Cutting-edge technology is at your fingertips, with features like Apple CarPlay, Android Auto, and the advanced CabinControl system, allowing you to seamlessly integrate your smartphone and control various vehicle functions with ease. The 160-Watt AM/FM/HD/SiriusXM Audio System delivers a premium listening experience, while the Blind Spot Information (BSI) System and Adaptive Cruise Control enhance your confidence and safety on the road.

Versatility is the Odyssey's middle name. The split-folding rear seats and power liftgate make loading and unloading a breeze, while the ample cargo space ensures you can bring along everything you need for your family's adventures. The available power moonroof adds an extra touch of open-air elegance to your driving experience.

Backed by Honda's renowned reputation for quality, reliability, and longevity, the 2023 Odyssey EX-L is the perfect companion for your growing family. Experience the difference for yourself and schedule a test drive today. We're confident you'll be impressed by this exceptional minivan's blend of practicality, technology, and refined style.

description:
Discover the ultimate family-friendly SUV with the 2023 Toyota Sienna XSE AWD 7 Passenger. This exceptional vehicle combines style, performance, and unparalleled versatility to elevate your driving experience.

Boasting a stunning exterior in a sleek White color, the Sienna XSE commands attention wherever it goes. Under the hood, the powerful 2.5L I4 engine paired with a smooth CVT and AWD system delivers exceptional fuel efficiency, with an impressive 35 city MPG and 36 highway MPG.

This Sienna is packed with an impressive array of features that cater to your every need:

• AWD/4X4
• ANDROID AUTO/APPLE CARPLAY
• LEATHER SEATS
• HEATED SEATS
• SUNROOF
• NAVIGATION
• BACKUP CAMERA
• PARKING PROXIMITY SENSORS
• PUSH BUTTON START
• POWER SEAT
• CRUISE CONTROL
• KEYLESS ENTRY

The XSE Plus Package further enhances your driving experience, offering a premium audio system, dual-zone climate control, and a host of advanced safety technologies.

Standout features include the intuitive navigation system, the impressive JBL audio system, and the convenient wireless charging pad. Dual-zone climate control, heated front seats, and a power moonroof add to the Sienna's luxurious cabin, while the rear dual-zone air conditioning ensures your passengers remain comfortable.

Safety is paramount, and the Sienna XSE delivers with a comprehensive suite of advanced driver-assistance features, including Lane Departure Warning, Automatic High Beams, and Rear Parking Sensors. The Blind Spot Monitoring and Rear Cross-Traffic Alert systems provide added peace of mind on the road.

With seating for up to 7 passengers and ample cargo space, the Sienna XSE is the perfect companion for your family adventures. Its versatile design and innovative features make it a standout in the minivan segment.

Experience the exceptional quality, performance, and technology of the 2023 Toyota Sienna XSE AWD 7 Passenger. Visit our showroom today and let us demonstrate why this vehicle is the perfect choice for your next family vehicle.

description: Discover the perfect balance of power, comfort, and convenience in the 2023 Honda Odyssey EX-L. This exceptional minivan is a true testament to Honda's commitment to engineering excellence, offering an unparalleled driving experience and a wealth of premium features that cater to your every need.Highlighted by a striking Silver exterior, the Odyssey EX-L boasts a suite of desirable amenities, including:Heated SeatsLeather SeatingBluetooth Audio StreamingBack Up CameraTraded in from Original OwnerGood and Bad Credit Programs Available - Ask us How!Service Contracts to 100,000 Miles Available!Beneath the sleek exterior lies a powerful 3.5L V6 SOHC i-VTEC 24V engine, mated to a smooth-shifting 10-Speed Automatic transmission, delivering an impressive fuel efficiency of 19 city / 28 highway MPG. This exceptional powertrain not only provides ample acceleration but also ensures a refined and responsive driving experience, making every journey a pleasure.Step inside the Odyssey EX-L and be captivated by the sophisticated and well-appointed cabin. The leather-wrapped steering wheel and heated front seats create an inviting and comfortable atmosphere, while the available power moonroof and power liftgate add a touch of modern convenience. The advanced infotainment system, complete with Apple CarPlay and Android Auto integration, keeps you seamlessly connected and entertained on the go.Safety is of paramount importance in the Odyssey, and this model is equipped with a comprehensive suite of advanced driver-assistance technologies. From the Blind Spot Information (BSI) System to the Lane Keeping Assist System (LKAS), you can navigate the roads with confidence, knowing that your family's well-being is prioritized.With a low mileage of just 19,441 and a wealth of service records available, this 2023 Honda Odyssey EX-L represents an exceptional value proposition. Whether you're in the market for a versatile family hauler or a reliable daily driver, this exceptional minivan is sure to exceed your expectations.We invite you to experience the exceptional qualities of the 2023 Honda Odyssey EX-L for yourself. Visit our showroom today and let our knowledgeable sales team guide you through the features and benefits of this remarkable vehicle. With a range of financing options and service contracts available, we're confident we can help you find the perfect solution to fit your needs and budget.

Experience the pinnacle of luxury and performance with this exquisite 2022 Genesis GV70 3.5T Sport. This Genesis Certified Pre-Owned vehicle boasts an impressive array of features that will captivate the discerning driver.

• FACTORY CERTIFIED PRE-OWNED VEHICLE!
• REAR VIEW BACK-UP CAMERA!
• BLUETOOTH HANDS-FREE CALLING!
• LEATHER SEATS!
• NON SMOKER!
• PANORAMIC MOONROOF!
• SPORT PRESTIGE PACKAGE
• Includes Features Not Included, Highway Driving Assist, Forward Collision-Avoidance Assist, Blind-Spot View Monitor, Front Parking Distance Warning, Genesis Digital Key, Rear Parking Collision-Avoidance Assist, Lexicon Premium Audio, Surround View Monitor, Heated Steering Wheel, Remote Smart Parking Assist, Acoustic Rear Door Glass, Carbon Fiber Trim, 3-Zone Climate, 21" Sport Dark Sputtering Alloy Wheels, Heated 2nd Row Seats, Heads-Up Display, Manual Rear Side Sunshades, Electronic Limited-Slip Differential, 12.3" 3D Digital Cluster

This Genesis GV70 3.5T Sport is a true testament to the brand's commitment to craftsmanship and performance. Powered by a robust 3.5L DOHC engine and equipped with an 8-speed automatic transmission, this all-wheel-drive SUV delivers an exhilarating driving experience. With an impressive 19 city/25 highway MPG, you'll enjoy exceptional fuel efficiency without sacrificing power.

Stepping inside, you'll be enveloped in a world of luxury and technology. The stunning Mauna Red interior, complete with leather seating surfaces and suede headliner, creates a sophisticated ambiance. The panoramic moonroof floods the cabin with natural light, while the 12.3" 3D digital cluster and Lexicon premium audio system provide an immersive multimedia experience.

Safety and convenience are also top priorities in this GV70. Features like the Surround View Monitor, Blind-Spot View Monitor, and Remote Smart Parking Assist ensure you can navigate with confidence, while the Heads-Up Display and Heated Steering Wheel add to the overall driving enjoyment.

As a Genesis Certified Pre-Owned vehicle, this GV70 3.5T Sport has undergone a rigorous 191-point inspection and comes with an impressive warranty coverage. Enjoy the peace of mind of a 72-month/75,000-mile limited warranty, a 120-month/100,000-mile powertrain warranty, and 10 years of unlimited-mile roadside assistance.

Don't miss your opportunity to experience the exceptional craftsmanship and performance of this 2022 Genesis GV70 3.5T Sport. Visit our showroom today and let us demonstrate how this remarkable SUV can elevate your driving experience.

This 2023 Toyota Sienna XLE, has a Wind Chill Pearl exterior and an Chateau interior color. 39,662 miles. Stock Number 250146B. You can connect with us by calling 518-793-3871. One Owner! OTHER NOTABLE FEATURES AND OPTIONS YOU SHOULD KNOW ABOUT: Safety and Security
  • Lane departure prevention - Keep it between the lines. It only takes a moment of inattention for your vehicle to drift. With lane departure prevention, your vehicle takes corrective action to help you avoid unintentionally moving out of your lane. Lane departure prevention is an extra level of safety for you and those around you.
  • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
  • Pedestrian impact prevention - An extra step toward safety. Pedestrians don't always stop, look, and listen, but with Pedestrian Impact Prevention, your vehicle is equipped to better see them and avoid them. This system constantly monitors the road ahead to identify and track pedestrians. It projects that image to an interior display screen, AND should an impact become likely, Pedestrian impact prevention takes steps to avoid a collision.
  • Hands-on cruise control. Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful. Cruise control only managed speed, but not distance or safety. Now, with hands-on cruise control, simply set your desired speed and let sensor technology maintain a safe distance between you and surrounding vehicles. It slows you down, speeds you up and even keeps you in your own lane. Meet your ultimate co-pilot with hands-on cruise control.
Technology and Telematics
  • Smart device mirroring - Smartphone, meet smart car. You can control your device through your vehicle's infotainment system. Smart device mirroring brings together safety and convenience by making it easier to find what you're looking for while keeping your eyes on the road.

description: Buckle up and get ready for a ride of pure luxury and comfort in this stunning White 2023 Honda Odyssey! This ultimate family-friendly vehicle is packed with all the bells and whistles you could ever dream of, making every journey a first-class experience.Step inside the spacious cabin and be greeted by a world of convenience and sophistication. Sink into the plush seats and grip the heated leather steering wheel, feeling the power of the 3.5L V6 engine ready to take you on your next adventure. With the 10-speed automatic transmission and paddle shifters, you'll experience smooth and effortless shifts as you cruise down the road with the front-wheel-drive capability.As you hit the road, enjoy the sunshine beaming through the express open/close sliding sunroof, adding a touch of luxury to your drive. The sleek design of the 19" alloy wheels with shark gray inserts will have heads turning as you make your way through town. And with the power sliding rear doors, loading and unloading your precious cargo has never been easier.Entertainment is taken to the next level with the premium audio system and multiple LCD monitors, keeping everyone in the vehicle entertained for the journey ahead. Plus, with features like adaptive cruise control and an advanced navigation system, you'll arrive at your destination with ease and in style.Safety is at the forefront of this Honda Odyssey, with a plethora of advanced features such as blind-spot monitoring, collision mitigation braking system, and front and rear parking sensors to keep you and your passengers protected at all times. The included Carfax report adds an extra layer of assurance, giving you peace of mind as you hit the road with your loved ones.So, if you're in the market for a versatile, stylish, and feature-packed minivan that caters to all your needs, look no further than this White 2023 Honda Odyssey. It's not just a car, it's a lifestyle upgrade, beckoning you to embark on unforgettable journeys and make memories that will last a lifetime.

Introducing the highly anticipated 2023 Honda Odyssey Touring! This ultimate family vehicle is designed to elevate your driving experience with its exceptional features and spacious interior.

With the Odyssey Touring, you can expect top-of-the-line performance thanks to its powerful V6 engine and smooth-shifting 10-speed automatic transmission. Plus, the advanced safety features such as the Honda Sensing suite and rearview camera will give you peace of mind while on the road.

If you’re looking for a comfortable, reliable, and incredibly practical family vehicle, this 2023 Honda Odyssey EX-L is a fantastic choice. The Odyssey is widely considered one of the best-driving minivans on the road thanks to its smooth ride, strong V6 power, and smart interior design.

⭐ Why Families Love the Odyssey EX-L

Leather interior

Tri-zone automatic climate control

The Odyssey is built to make daily life easier — from school drop-offs and road trips to grocery runs and weekend adventures. The interior is thoughtfully designed with excellent visibility and flexible seating.

With 34k miles, this Odyssey EX-L has been well cared for and still offers outstanding long-term value.

If you want a clean, well-equipped minivan with comfort, space, and proven reliability, this 2023 Honda Odyssey EX-L is absolutely worth a closer look.

Why BUY from Jacobs Motors? When you choose this Luxury White Pearlcoat 2022 Jeep Wagoneer Series III with 71,816 miles, you are not just buying a used vehicle - you are investing in quality, reliability and peace of mind. Our clientele depend on us for Transparent Pricing, Convenience and, most importantly, Customer FIRST Service! No Accidents! What this vehicle includes: Quick Order Package 22N
    Comfort
    • Ventilated front seats -That's cool. Ventilated front seats provides targeted cool air so you and your passenger can get comfortable quicker in hot weather. Getting comfortable is no sweat when you have ventilated front seats.
    Convenience
    • Power open and close liftgate - On-demand access. When your arms are full of cargo, the last thing you want to do is set it all down just to open the liftgate, then pick it all back up to load it in. By remotely opening and closing, power liftgate lets you skip straight to the loading. It also eliminates the awkward stretch to reach up for the liftgate to close it. Load and go with power open and close liftgate.
    • Keyfob engine start control - Get an early start. Remotely start your vehicle's engine from the key fob, ensuring your ride is ready to go when you get in. Now you can stay comfortable inside while your vehicle gets comfortable outside, thanks to Keyfob engine start control.
    Safety and Security
    • Blind spot warning - Protect your blind side. You checked the mirror, looked over your shoulder and still nearly collided with the car next to you. Blind spot warning alerts you to the presence of a vehicle to your sides or rear so you know if you're about to make an unsafe lane change. Replace fear and uncertainty with confidence and safety with blind spot warning.
    Technology and Telematics
    • Voice activated integrated navigation system - A to B made easy! Whether it's an errand or a road trip, the voice activated integrated navigation system will guide you to your destination. No more bulky, impossible-to-fold maps, and no more stopping to ask for directions. Just tell it where you want to go, and the voice activated integrated navigation system shows you the right way.

CarFax No Accidents! CarFax One Owner! Popular Options and Features Include: Safety and Security
  • An active lane departure system alerts the driver of unintended movement of the vehicle out of a designated traffic lane and automatically maintains the vehicle's position within that lane.
  • The vehicle is equipped with a system that senses, and then prepares, the vehicle and/or occupants, for an impending forward collision.
  • The vehicle constantly monitors the roadway in front of the vehicle and identifies and tracks pedestrians on an interior display. If the system determines a likely impact, it will automatically take preventative steps to avoid hitting the pedestrian.
  • With this system the driver's hands must remain on the wheel at all times but can be removed briefly (for a few seconds), otherwise the vehicle will prompt the driver to put their hands back on the wheel.
  • The vehicle is equipped with a camera that displays an image of the area behind the vehicle on an interior display.
Technology and Telematics
  • Without the need for a manufacturer specific app to be installed on the smart device, the vehicle infotainment system can access and control functions of a smart device physically plugged-into the vehicle.
  • Mobile devices can wirelessly connect to the internet through the vehicle's private mobile network.

- Storage: Configurable second row, 60/40 split and stowable third row with one-motion stow

- Tech: 9-inch touchscreen with Apple CarPlay and Android Auto, SiriusXM 3-month Platinum trial, and 6 USB charge ports

- Comfort: Three-zone automatic climate control with rear cabin controls and power driver seat

- Safety: Toyota Safety Sense 2.0 including Pre-Collision System with Pedestrian Detection, Full-Speed Dynamic Radar Cruise Control, Lane Departure Alert with Steering Assist, Lane Tracing Assist, Blind Spot Monitor with Rear Cross-Traffic Alert

Ownership includes our Car Doc maintenance plan with 6 complimentary oil changes and 6 complimentary tire rotations during the first two years. Upgrade to a 3-year or 5-year Car Doc plan for added perks and protection.

We are in the business of building relationships, not just selling vehicles.

This well-equipped Toyota Sienna was recently acquired to our store here in St. Louis!

The Toyota Sienna LE Hybrid focuses on space, comfort, and family utility. The Ash fabric interior and 8-passenger seating configuration make daily driving, commuting, and road trips simple and comfortable.

Key Features

- 2.5L 4-Cylinder Hybrid System producing 245 combined net horsepower

- Front-Wheel Drive (FWD) with smooth and efficient Electronic CVT

- 8-Passenger Seating with second-row bench and one-motion stow third row

- Dual Power Sliding Side Doors for easy access

- Flexible Interior Storage with fold-flat seating and smart cargo solutions

- 9-inch Touchscreen Display with Apple CarPlay & Android Auto and multiple USB ports

- Three-Zone Automatic Climate Control with rear cabin controls

- Toyota Safety Sense 2.0, including adaptive cruise control, lane tracing assist, pre-collision braking with pedestrian detection, blind spot monitoring, and rear cross-traffic alert

We just completed our Victory 182-Point Inspection, performed a full maintenance and battery check, topped off all fluids, and completed a full interior and exterior detail. Two keys included.

description: Introducing the 2024 Kia Carnival SX Prestige - a versatile and feature-rich minivan that's ready to elevate your driving experience. With its sleek exterior, powerful V6 engine, and a host of advanced technologies, this Carnival is the perfect companion for your family's adventures.Backup CameraBluetoothNavigation SystemBlue Exterior ColorCarpeted Floor Mats (8-Passenger)Boasting a striking Astra Blue exterior, this Carnival commands attention on the road. But its true essence lies in the exceptional features that set it apart. The Navigation System will guide you effortlessly, while the Heated and Ventilated Front Bucket Seats ensure your comfort mile after mile. The Power Moonroof and Power Liftgate add a touch of convenience, while Apple CarPlay and Android Auto seamlessly integrate your smartphone.Under the hood, the 8-Speed Automatic Transmission and Front-Wheel Drive deliver a smooth and responsive ride, with an impressive fuel efficiency of 19 MPG in the city and 26 MPG on the highway. Whether you're navigating the daily commute or embarking on a family road trip, this Carnival has the power and efficiency to keep you moving.But the true essence of this vehicle lies in its versatility. The Split Folding Rear Seat and Power 2nd-Row Moonroof offer unparalleled flexibility, allowing you to customize the cabin to suit your needs. And with the Rear Window Wiper and Variably Intermittent Wipers, you can conquer any weather condition with ease.Safety is also a top priority in the Carnival SX Prestige. The advanced safety features, including the Dual Front Impact Airbags, Dual Front Side Impact Airbags, and Electronic Stability Control, provide you and your loved ones with the protection you deserve.As you step inside, you'll be greeted by the premium Pure Leather Seat Trim and the Heated Steering Wheel, creating a luxurious and comfortable environment. The Tilt and Telescoping Steering Wheel, along with the Steering Wheel Mounted Audio Controls, allow you to stay in command of your driving experience.This 2024 Kia Carnival SX Prestige is a true standout in the minivan segment. With its exceptional features, impressive performance, and unparalleled versatility, it's the perfect choice for discerning families who demand the best. Experience the difference for yourself and schedule a test drive today. We're confident you'll be impressed by the Carnival's capabilities and eager to make it your own.

  • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
  • Pedestrian impact prevention - An extra step toward safety. Pedestrians don't always stop, look, and listen, but with Pedestrian Impact Prevention, your vehicle is equipped to better see them and avoid them. This system constantly monitors the road ahead to identify and track pedestrians. It projects that image to an interior display screen, AND should an impact become likely, Pedestrian impact prevention takes steps to avoid a collision.
  • Rear camera - Watching your back! The rear camera helps you see obstacles and hazards you otherwise couldn't by showing enhanced images of what is behind you. The rear camera is an extra set of eyes that's both convenient and safe.
  • Lane departure prevention - Keep it between the lines. It only takes a moment of inattention for your vehicle to drift. With lane departure prevention, your vehicle takes corrective action to help you avoid unintentionally moving out of your lane. Lane departure prevention is an extra level of safety for you and those around you.
Technology and Telematics
  • Smart device mirroring - Smartphone, meet smart car. You can control your device through your vehicle's infotainment system. Smart device mirroring brings together safety and convenience by making it easier to find what you're looking for while keeping your eyes on the road.

description:
Check out this 2024 Toyota Sienna LE finished in Midnight Black Metallic with a GRAY interior. This vehicle is equipped with the following features and options: Convenience
  • Distance pacing cruise control with traffic stop-go. Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful. Cruise control only managed speed, but not distance or safety. Now, with Distance pacing cruise control with traffic stop-go, simply set your desired speed and let sensor technology maintain a safe distance between you and the vehicle ahead. It's stop/go feature automatically brings the vehicle to a stop if traffic stops and resumes distance pacing cruise when traffic starts to move again. Distance pacing cruise control with traffic stop-go, your ultimate co-pilot.
  • Cruise control with steering wheel mounted controls. Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful, until cruise control set the pace. Simply set the desired speed using the steering wheel mounted controls and it will maintain that speed without driver intervention. This can help minimize driver fatigue and improve overall fuel economy. Resting your right foot is right at your fingertips thanks to cruise control with steering wheel mounted controls.
Safety and Security
  • Hands-on cruise control. Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful. Cruise control only managed speed, but not distance or safety. Now, with hands-on cruise control, simply set your desired speed and let sensor technology maintain a safe distance between you and surrounding vehicles. It slows you down, speeds you up and even keeps you in your own lane. Meet your ultimate co-pilot with hands-on cruise control.
  • Lane departure prevention - Keep it between the lines. It only takes a moment of inattention for your vehicle to drift. With lane departure prevention, your vehicle takes corrective action to help you avoid unintentionally moving out of your lane. Lane departure prevention is an extra level of safety for you and those around you.
  • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
  • Pedestrian impact prevention - An extra step toward safety. Pedestrians don't always stop, look, and listen, but with Pedestrian Impact Prevention, your vehicle is equipped to better see them and avoid them. This system constantly monitors the road ahead to identify and track pedestrians. It projects that image to an interior display screen, AND should an impact become likely, Pedestrian impact prevention takes steps to avoid a collision.
  • Rear camera - Watching your back! The rear camera helps you see obstacles and hazards you otherwise couldn't by showing enhanced images of what is behind you. The rear camera is an extra set of eyes that's both convenient and safe.
  • Predictive brake assist - Be prepared for your big brake. Predictive brake assist monitors the available distance in front of you compared to your vehicles speed. If your speed exceeds the required distance to stop short of a collision, it readies your brakes to apply maximum stopping force when you use them. Predictive brake assist helps see to it that you stop.
Technology and Telematics
  • Smart device mirroring - Smartphone, meet smart car. You can control your device through your vehicle's infotainment system. Smart device mirroring brings together safety and convenience by making it easier to find what you're looking for while keeping your eyes on the road.
  • Mobile hotspot - WiFi on the fly. Connect your devices to the Internet through your vehicle's private mobile hotspot and take the internet wherever your journey takes you, without eating up your data allowance. Find the hotspot with mobile hotspot.

Discover the exceptional 2026 Chrysler Pacifica Select, a versatile and well-equipped family-friendly vehicle that seamlessly blends style, comfort, and advanced technology. With its sleek black exterior and impressive 3.6L V6 engine, this Pacifica is poised to deliver an exceptional driving experience.

Highlighted features include:

• 125 Point Inspection
• Fresh Trade-In
• Fully Inspected
• SAFETY SPHERE with ParkSense Front/Rear Park Assist and 360 Surround View Camera System
• 18" Polished Aluminum Wheels with Pirelli Self-Sealing Tires

This Chrysler Pacifica Select comes equipped with a wealth of premium amenities to elevate your daily drives, such as dual-zone automatic climate control, a heated steering wheel, and a 10.1" touchscreen display with Apple CarPlay and Android Auto integration.

As a Chrysler Certified Pre-Owned vehicle, this Pacifica has undergone a rigorous 125-point inspection and reconditioning process using authentic Mopar parts. It also comes with a comprehensive warranty package, including a 3-month/3,000-mile limited warranty after the original factory warranty expires, as well as a 12-month/12,000-mile extended care premium warranty. Additionally, you'll enjoy the peace of mind of roadside assistance, a car rental allowance, and a 3-month trial subscription to SiriusXM Guardian and satellite radio.

Combining exceptional value, uncompromising safety, and a wealth of cutting-edge features, the 2026 Chrysler Pacifica Select is the perfect choice for discerning families seeking a versatile and well-equipped vehicle. Experience the difference for yourself and schedule a test drive today.

Comfortable and confident, our One Owner 2023 Chrysler Pacifica Touring L Minivan AWD in Bright White helps you take on the daily grind and win! Powered by a 3.6 Liter Pentastar V6 that serves up 287hp to a 9 Speed Automatic transmission for family-focused capability. This All Wheel Drive minivan also sees nearly 25mpg on the highway with athletically sophisticated good looks. Premium Pacifica details include LED lighting, fog lamps, power-sliding side doors, a power liftgate, heated power mirrors, and alloy wheels.

Our Touring L cabin levels up with top-shelf features such as heated leatherette front seats, eight-way power for the driver, Stow 'n Go second and third rows, a heated TechnoLeather steering wheel, tri-zone automatic climate control, remote start, keyless access/ignition, and a super convenient Super Console. Family safety is non-negotiable, so Chrysler helps protect you with front/rear automatic braking, forward collision warning, adaptive cruise control, blind-spot monitoring, a rearview camera, lane-departure warning, and other smart technologies. With all that, our Pacifica Touring L is the minivan that makes a difference! Save this Page and Call for Availability. We Know You Will Enjoy Your Test Drive Towards Ownership! *Lowest prices reflect rewards discount, see dealer for details.

Discover the perfect blend of style, comfort, and versatility in this 2023 Chrysler Pacifica Touring L w/3rd Row Seats. This certified pre-owned minivan is a true standout, offering an exceptional driving experience and a wealth of premium features to elevate your daily commute or family adventures.

Highlighted by its Granite Crystal Metallic Clearcoat exterior and Gray interior, this Pacifica Touring L boasts an impressive array of amenities:

• Granite Crystal Metallic Clearcoat
• Quick Order Package 27L

• AM/FM radio: SiriusXM
• Radio: Uconnect 5 w/10.1" Display

• Power Liftgate

• 125 Point Inspection

• Vehicles Up to 75,000 Miles and/or 5 Model Years. 24-Hour Towing & Roadside Assistance, Car Rental Allowance, CARFAX® Vehicle History Report™ and an Introductory 3-month Subscription to SiriusXM® Satellite Radio & Certified Warranty Upgrades

Experience the exceptional value and peace of mind that comes with this certified pre-owned 2023 Chrysler Pacifica Touring L w/3rd Row Seats. Visit our showroom today and let us demonstrate why this versatile and well-equipped minivan is the perfect choice for your family's needs.
