description:
Discover the perfect balance of style, comfort, and technology in the 2023 Chrysler Pacifica Touring L. This exceptional minivan is a true standout, blending sleek design, impressive performance, and a wealth of advanced features to elevate your driving experience.

• 3rd Row Seating
• Heated Seats
• Heated Steering Wheel
• Remote Keyless Entry
• Push-Button Start
• Hands-Free Bluetooth
• Apple CarPlay/Android Auto
• Power Liftgate
• Rear Backup Camera
• Factory Alloy Wheels
• Intelligent Forward Collision Warning
• Automatic Emergency Braking with Pedestrian Detection
• Blind Spot Warning
• Rain-Sensing Wipers

The Pacifica Touring L's 3.6L V6 engine and 9-speed automatic transmission deliver a smooth, responsive ride, while the FWD system provides confident handling on the open road. With an impressive 19 city/28 highway MPG, this minivan offers exceptional efficiency to keep your adventures going.

Step inside and discover a cabin that's both stylish and practical. Caprice Leatherette Bucket Seats provide all-day comfort, while the 10.1-inch Uconnect 5 touchscreen display puts a wealth of connectivity and entertainment features at your fingertips. The Pacifica Touring L also boasts a wealth of advanced safety technologies, including Blind Spot Monitoring, Rear Cross-Traffic Alert, and Lane Departure Warning, ensuring you and your family travel with confidence.

Whether you're transporting the kids to their activities, embarking on a family road trip, or simply running errands around town, the 2023 Chrysler Pacifica Touring L is the perfect companion. With its exceptional versatility, cutting-edge technology, and refined driving dynamics, this minivan is sure to exceed your expectations.

Experience the difference for yourself by scheduling a test drive at our showroom. We're confident you'll be impressed by the Pacifica Touring L's unbeatable combination of style, capability, and value. Let us help you discover the perfect vehicle to elevate your daily drives and create lasting memories with your loved ones.

description:
Experience the epitome of family luxury with the 2023 Chrysler Pacifica Limited. This exceptional minivan is designed to elevate your daily drives and create unforgettable moments on the road.

Boasting an impressive array of premium features, the Pacifica Limited sets the standard for modern family transportation. Indulge in the comfort of its ✓ Nappa Leather Bucket Seats, ✓ Heated and Ventilated Front Seats, and ✓ Heated Rear Seats, ensuring everyone travels in absolute bliss. The ✓ Power Folding 3rd Row Seat and ✓ Split Folding Rear Seat offer unparalleled versatility, allowing you to effortlessly adapt the interior to your needs.

Elevate your driving experience with the Pacifica Limited's advanced technology. Enjoy the convenience of ✓ Factory GPS Navigation, ✓ Wireless Charging Pad, and ✓ Apple CarPlay/Android Auto, seamlessly integrating your digital world. Stay connected with the ✓ WiFi Hotspot and ✓ SiriusXM Satellite Radio, providing endless entertainment options.

Safety is of the utmost importance, and the Pacifica Limited delivers with an impressive array of advanced driver-assistance features. ✓ Adaptive Cruise Control with Stop & Go, ✓ Automatic Emergency Braking with Pedestrian Detection, and ✓ Blind Spot Warning ensure you and your loved ones arrive at your destination with confidence.

Indulge in the luxury of the ✓ Power Sunroof/Moonroof, allowing you to bask in the natural light and enjoy the great outdoors from the comfort of your Pacifica. The ✓ Power Liftgate and ✓ Rear Backup Camera further enhance the convenience and functionality of this exceptional minivan.

With its stunning ✓ Velvet Red Pearlcoat exterior and ✓ 18" Painted Aluminum Wheels, the Pacifica Limited exudes a refined and sophisticated presence. This minivan is not just a practical choice, it's a statement of style and sophistication.

You'll find Nissan South Morrow conveniently situated just off Interstate 75 South at 6889 Jonesboro Rd, Morrow, GA. Our dealership boasts the latest Nissan models as well as a diverse selection of top-notch pre-owned vehicles. The finance department is ready to offer you some fantastic and affordable payment options, and we take pride in our professionally trained service and parts center, where we're fully equipped to cater to all your automotive needs. If you're in the market for a new or pre-owned Nissan with low monthly payments, we are genuinely thrilled to invite you to pay us a visit. Let's work together to find the perfect car, truck, SUV, or minivan for you!

We want to ensure you have all the details you need! Our pricing and information are presented with utmost accuracy. Please keep in mind that prices and incentives can vary depending on your location, and they are subject to change.     • Manual fold into floor second-row seat - Room to move! When you need the extra space for cargo rather than kids, you'll love the manual fold-into-floor second row seats. Just pull the release and manual fold into floor second-row seats disappear for more room in the back, without hurting your back.

Just pull the release and manual fold into floor second-row seats disappear for more room in the back, without hurting your back.
    • Stow 'n Go manual fold-into-floor folding second-row seats
    • Heated steering wheel - A warm touch. Trying to drive with bulky winter gloves on isn't always easy. Keep your hands warm in cold temperatures so you can ditch the mitts and get a firm grip with this heated steering wheel.
    • Heated driver and front passenger seat cushions - That's hot. Heated driver and front passenger seat cushions provide more targeted warmth so you can get comfortable quicker in cold weather. If you have lower body pain, you might also be soothed by the heat while you drive. No matter the weather, find comfort in heated driver and front passenger seat cushions.
    • This upholstery simulates leather, is durable and easy to keep clean.
    • 8-way driver seat - Comfort that conforms to you! It doesn't matter how long your drive is, if you aren't comfortable while you're behind the wheel, every trip feels like a chore. With 8-way driver seat, finding the perfect position is easy, so you can sit back, (or up, or a little forward), relax and enjoy the journey.
    • Front passenger seat with 4-way directional controls
    • Heated driver and front passenger seat cushions - That's hot. Heated driver and front passenger seat cushions provide more targeted warmth so you can get comfortable quicker in cold weather. If you have lower body pain, you might also be soothed by the heat while you drive. No matter the weather, find comfort in heated driver and front passenger seat cushions.
    Convenience
    • Power open and close liftgate - On-demand access. When your arms are full of cargo, the last thing you want to do is set it all down just to open the liftgate, then pick it all back up to load it in. By remotely opening and closing, power liftgate lets you skip straight to the loading. It also eliminates the awkward stretch to reach up for the liftgate to close it. Load and go with power open and close liftgate.
    • Keyfob engine start control - Get an early start. Remotely start your vehicle's engine from the key fob, ensuring your ride is ready to go when you get in. Now you can stay comfortable inside while your vehicle gets comfortable outside, thanks to Keyfob engine start control.
    • Keyfob cargo access control - Load up without the set down. With keyfob cargo access control, packing up your vehicle is easy. The keyfob unlocks the cargo door or lid so you don't have to set your cargo down, unlock, then pick your cargo back up before you load it in. With just a push of a button, the cargo area is ready for your stuff. Keyfob cargo access control helps you take a load off.
    • Distance pacing cruise control with traffic stop-go. Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful. Cruise control only managed speed, but not distance or safety. Now, with Distance pacing cruise control with traffic stop-go, simply set your desired speed and let sensor technology maintain a safe distance between you and the vehicle ahead. It's stop/go feature automatically brings the vehicle to a stop if traffic stops and resumes distance pacing cruise when traffic starts to move again. Distance pacing cruise control with traffic stop-go, your ultimate co-pilot.
    • Cruise control with steering wheel mounted controls. Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful, until cruise control set the pace. Simply set the desired speed using the steering wheel mounted controls and it will maintain that speed without driver intervention. This can help minimize driver fatigue and improve overall fuel economy. Resting your right foot is right at your fingertips thanks to cruise control with steering wheel mounted controls.
    Safety and Security
    • Blind spot warning - Protect your blind side. You checked the mirror, looked over your shoulder and still nearly collided with the car next to you. Blind spot warning alerts you to the presence of a vehicle to your sides or rear so you know if you're about to make an unsafe lane change. Replace fear and uncertainty with confidence and safety with blind spot warning.
    • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
    • Pedestrian impact prevention - An extra step toward safety. Pedestrians don't always stop, look, and listen, but with Pedestrian Impact Prevention, your vehicle is equipped to better see them and avoid them. This system constantly monitors the road ahead to identify and track pedestrians. It projects that image to an interior display screen, AND should an impact become likely, Pedestrian impact prevention takes steps to avoid a collision.
    • Rear camera - Watching your back! The rear camera helps you see obstacles and hazards you otherwise couldn't by showing enhanced images of what is behind you. The rear camera is an extra set of eyes that's both convenient and safe.
    • Rear camera - Watching your back! The rear camera helps you see obstacles and hazards you otherwise couldn't by showing enhanced images of what is behind you. The rear camera is an extra set of eyes that's both convenient and safe.
    • Lane departure prevention - Keep it between the lines. It only takes a moment of inattention for your vehicle to drift. With lane departure prevention, your vehicle takes corrective action to help you avoid unintentionally moving out of your lane. Lane departure prevention is an extra level of safety for you and those around you.
    • Brake assist - Stop right there. Something jumps out into the middle of the road and you need to stop now! With brake assist, you will. It uses the speed of the brake pedal's travel to sense panic braking, then applies all available power to boost your stopping power. Brake assist can stop the accident before it is one.
    Technology and Telematics
    • Smart device mirroring - Smartphone, meet smart car. You can control your device through your vehicle's infotainment system. Smart device mirroring brings together safety and convenience by making it easier to find what you're looking for while keeping your eyes on the road.
    • Apple CarPlay/Android Auto smart device wireless mirroring
    • Wireless connectivity - Strike the cord. Wireless technology makes it easy to place calls without having to fumble with your phone. It integrates your device with the system inside your vehicle for hands-free access. Keep connected and keep your hands on the wheel with wireless connectivity.
    • 10 USB ports - No adaptor needed! You need a charge. You want to hear your music. But your adapter is lost and all you have is a USB cord. That's A-Okay - with 10 USB ports, you can connect, power up and go.

The keyfob unlocks the cargo door or lid so you don't have to set your cargo down, unlock, then pick your cargo back up before you load it in. With just a push of a button, the cargo area is ready for your stuff. Keyfob cargo access control helps you take a load off.
    • Distance pacing cruise control with traffic stop-go. Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful. Cruise control only managed speed, but not distance or safety. Now, with Distance pacing cruise control with traffic stop-go, simply set your desired speed and let sensor technology maintain a safe distance between you and the vehicle ahead. It's stop/go feature automatically brings the vehicle to a stop if traffic stops and resumes distance pacing cruise when traffic starts to move again. Distance pacing cruise control with traffic stop-go, your ultimate co-pilot.
    • Cruise control with steering wheel mounted controls. Set it and forget it. Road trips used to be stressful, until cruise control set the pace. Simply set the desired speed using the steering wheel mounted controls and it will maintain that speed without driver intervention. This can help minimize driver fatigue and improve overall fuel economy. Resting your right foot is right at your fingertips thanks to cruise control with steering wheel mounted controls.
    Safety and Security
    • Blind spot warning - Protect your blind side. You checked the mirror, looked over your shoulder and still nearly collided with the car next to you. Blind spot warning alerts you to the presence of a vehicle to your sides or rear so you know if you're about to make an unsafe lane change. Replace fear and uncertainty with confidence and safety with blind spot warning.
    • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
    • Pedestrian impact prevention - An extra step toward safety. Pedestrians don't always stop, look, and listen, but with Pedestrian Impact Prevention, your vehicle is equipped to better see them and avoid them. This system constantly monitors the road ahead to identify and track pedestrians. It projects that image to an interior display screen, AND should an impact become likely, Pedestrian impact prevention takes steps to avoid a collision.
    • Rear camera - Watching your back! The rear camera helps you see obstacles and hazards you otherwise couldn't by showing enhanced images of what is behind you. The rear camera is an extra set of eyes that's both convenient and safe.
    • Rear camera - Watching your back! The rear camera helps you see obstacles and hazards you otherwise couldn't by showing enhanced images of what is behind you. The rear camera is an extra set of eyes that's both convenient and safe.
    • Lane departure prevention - Keep it between the lines. It only takes a moment of inattention for your vehicle to drift. With lane departure prevention, your vehicle takes corrective action to help you avoid unintentionally moving out of your lane. Lane departure prevention is an extra level of safety for you and those around you.
    • Brake assist - Stop right there. Something jumps out into the middle of the road and you need to stop now! With brake assist, you will. It uses the speed of the brake pedal's travel to sense panic braking, then applies all available power to boost your stopping power. Brake assist can stop the accident before it is one.
    Technology and Telematics
    • Smart device mirroring - Smartphone, meet smart car. You can control your device through your vehicle's infotainment system. Smart device mirroring brings together safety and convenience by making it easier to find what you're looking for while keeping your eyes on the road.
    • Apple CarPlay/Android Auto smart device wireless mirroring
    • Wireless connectivity - Strike the cord. Wireless technology makes it easy to place calls without having to fumble with your phone. It integrates your device with the system inside your vehicle for hands-free access. Keep connected and keep your hands on the wheel with wireless connectivity.
    • 10 USB ports - No adaptor needed! You need a charge. You want to hear your music. But your adapter is lost and all you have is a USB cord. That's A-Okay - with 10 USB ports, you can connect, power up and go.

Whether its school-run mornings or road-trip weekends, this Pacifica brings comfort, clever design, and better fuel economy to every mile. Plug-In Hybrid Power Efficiency At the heart of this Pacifica is a 3.6L Pentastar V6 plug-in hybrid powertrain paired with a smooth CVT automatic transmission, generating a combined 260 horsepower with strong responsiveness for highway merging and everyday driving. All-Electric Capability: Up to 32 miles of pure electric driving, ideal for commute-only days without using gas. Impressive Efficiency: Around 82 MPGe in electric/hybrid mode and 30 MPG once battery is depleted, letting you save at the pump without sacrificing performance. Seamless Hybrid Transitions: The minivan switches fluidly between electric and gas power for a refined and quiet ride. Comfort Space for All Step inside and youll find a thoughtfully crafted interior designed for families and adventurers alike: Seats up to 7 passengers with supportive, comfortable seating. Leather-trimmed comfort and premium touches that elevate the cabin feel. Tri-zone climate control keeps everyone comfortable from front to back. Flexible cargo space: 32.3 cu ft behind the third row expands dramatically when folded for road trips or gear hauling. Family-friendly details, like ambient lighting and easy-to-reach storage, make every drive more convenient. Tech That Makes Life Easier Stay connected and entertained with a suite of modern tech: Uconnect 5 with a 10.1 touchscreen crisp graphics and intuitive controls. Wireless Apple CarPlay Android Auto connect your smartphone seamlessly. Six-speaker audio system and SiriusXM satellite radio for music, news, and entertainment. Multiple USB ports keep devices charged throughout the cabin. Safety Peace of Mind The Touring L comes equipped with a comprehensive suite of advanced safety tech to protect you and your loved ones: Blind-spot monitoring rear cross-traffic alert Forward collision warning with active braking Adaptive cruise control Rear ParkSense assistance and a rearview camera All helping you feel confident on busy streets and long highways. Style With Purpose With distinctive hybrid badging, LED lighting, and stylish accents, the Pacifica Hybrid Touring L stands out in the minivan segment while offering practicality and refined design that families appreciate. Bottom Line The 2023 Chrysler Pacifica Hybrid Touring L is more than just a minivan its a family-ready, eco-smart, tech-savvy vehicle that makes every journey comfortable, efficient, and enjoyable. Whether youre commuting, carpooling, or cruising cross-country, this plug-in hybrid brings efficiency, comfort, and peace of mind to every mile.

Elevate your daily commute with the 2023 Chrysler Voyager LX. This versatile minivan offers a winning combination of style, comfort, and cutting-edge technology, making it the perfect companion for your busy lifestyle.

• Quick Order Package 27E

Powered by a robust 3.6L V6 engine and equipped with a smooth-shifting 9-speed automatic transmission, the Voyager LX delivers impressive fuel efficiency, with an EPA-estimated 19 city/28 highway MPG. Its spacious interior, with seating for up to 7, offers ample room for passengers and cargo, making it the perfect choice for families or those with an active lifestyle.

The Voyager LX comes loaded with a wealth of premium features, including a stunning 7-inch Uconnect 5 display with Apple CarPlay and Google Android Auto integration, allowing you to seamlessly connect your smartphone and access your favorite apps on the go. The dual-zone automatic climate control, heated front seats, and power liftgate add an extra touch of convenience, while the comprehensive suite of advanced safety technologies, including ParkView Rear Back-Up Camera and Electronic Stability Control, provide you with peace of mind on the road.

Elevate your driving experience with the 2023 Chrysler Voyager LX. This exceptional minivan offers the perfect blend of style, performance, and cutting-edge technology, making it the ideal choice for those who demand more from their daily driver. Visit us today and discover the Voyager LX for yourself.

Call us now at (901)854-5337 or visit us at the corner of 385 and Byhalia in Collierville.

description:
Experience the pinnacle of family-friendly luxury with the 2023 Chrysler Pacifica Touring L. This exceptional minivan boasts a sleek, sophisticated design and a wealth of cutting-edge features that cater to your every need.

• One Owner
• Quick Order Package 27L

Slip behind the wheel and be captivated by the Pacifica's impressive performance. Powered by a robust 3.6L V6 24V VVT engine paired with a 9-Speed 948TE Automatic transmission, this minivan delivers an exceptional blend of power and efficiency, with an EPA-estimated 19 city/28 highway MPG.

Elevate your driving experience with the Pacifica's array of premium amenities. Enjoy the comfort of heated front seats, a heated steering wheel, and dual-zone automatic climate control, ensuring everyone on board is perfectly content. The 10.1" touchscreen display with Uconnect 5 and Apple CarPlay/Android Auto integration keeps you seamlessly connected and entertained.

Safety is paramount in the Pacifica Touring L. Equipped with advanced driver-assistance technologies, including ParkView Rear Back-Up Camera, Brake Assist, and Electronic Stability Control, you can navigate the roads with confidence and peace of mind.

Versatility is at the heart of the Pacifica, with a split-folding third-row seat and a power liftgate that make loading and unloading a breeze. Whether you're transporting the whole family or tackling your weekend adventures, this minivan is ready to accommodate your every need.

Experience the ultimate in family-focused luxury with the 2023 Chrysler Pacifica Touring L. Visit our showroom today and discover how this exceptional minivan can elevate your driving experience.

description:
Discover the exceptional 2023 Chrysler Pacifica Touring L, a versatile and well-equipped minivan that offers the perfect blend of style, comfort, and technology. With its sleek white exterior and powerful 3.6L V6 engine, this Pacifica is not only visually appealing but also delivers impressive performance and efficiency, boasting 19 city and 28 highway MPG.

Highlighted features that make this Pacifica a standout include:

• Handsfree Bluetooth
• USB Port
• Quick Order Package 27L
• Integrated Active Noise Cancellation
• Uconnect 5 with 10.1" Touchscreen Display
• Apple CarPlay and Android Auto
• Heated Steering Wheel
• Reclining 3rd Row Seat
• Power Liftgate
• ParkView Rear Back-Up Camera
• Electronic Stability Control
• 17" Aluminum Wheels

Step inside and experience the exceptional comfort and convenience of the Pacifica Touring L. The spacious interior, with its premium Caprice Leatherette Bucket Seats and split-folding third-row, offers ample room for passengers and cargo alike. The dual-zone automatic climate control and heated front seats ensure a comfortable ride, no matter the weather.

The advanced Uconnect 5 infotainment system, complete with a stunning 10.1" touchscreen display, provides seamless integration of your smartphone's apps and features through Apple CarPlay and Android Auto. Stay connected and entertained throughout your journeys.

Safety is paramount in the Pacifica Touring L, which comes equipped with a suite of advanced driver-assist technologies, including Blind Spot Monitoring, Rear Cross-Traffic Alert, and Forward Collision Warning with Automatic Emergency Braking. Whether you're transporting the family, embarking on a road trip, or simply seeking a versatile and well-appointed minivan, the 2023 Chrysler Pacifica Touring L is the perfect choice. Experience the exceptional craftsmanship, technology, and capability that make this Pacifica a standout in its class. Visit our showroom today and let us demonstrate how this remarkable vehicle can enhance your driving experience.

Discover the ultimate family-friendly vehicle in the 2023 Chrysler Pacifica Touring L. This captivating minivan offers unparalleled versatility, cutting-edge technology, and a refined driving experience that will elevate your daily commute and weekend adventures.

Boasting a stunning Ceramic Gray Clearcoat exterior and a sophisticated Gray interior, this Pacifica Touring L is a true head-turner. Equipped with a powerful 3.6L V6 24V VVT engine and a smooth-shifting 9-Speed 948TE Automatic transmission, it delivers an exceptional blend of performance and efficiency, with an impressive 19 city/28 highway MPG rating.

• 1 Owner Clean CarFax
• Quick Order Package 27L

The Pacifica Touring L is packed with an array of premium features that will delight you and your passengers:

• 10.1" Touchscreen Display
• Apple CarPlay
• Heated Front Seats
• Power Liftgate
• ParkView Rear Back-Up Camera
• Integrated Active Noise Cancellation
• Automatic Temperature Control
• Remote Keyless Entry
• Steering Wheel Mounted Audio Controls

Experience the ultimate in comfort and convenience with the Pacifica Touring L's spacious and well-appointed interior. The split-folding third-row seat, Reclining 3rd Row Seat, and Caprice Leatherette Bucket Seats provide ample room for your family and cargo, while the Integrated Center Stack Radio, Disassociated Touchscreen Display, and Apple CarPlay seamlessly integrate your digital lifestyle.

Safety is also a top priority, with features like Dual Front Impact Airbags, Dual Front Side Impact Airbags, Knee Airbag, Electronic Stability Control, and a Rear Back-Up Camera ensuring your peace of mind on the road.

Don't miss your chance to own this exceptional 2023 Chrysler Pacifica Touring L. Schedule a test drive today and discover the perfect blend of style, technology, and family-friendly functionality. We look forward to welcoming you to our showroom and helping you find the vehicle that truly fits your lifestyle.

description:
**HONDA CERTIFIED** Thank you for choosing Classic Honda, this Crystal Black Pearl 2023 Honda Odyssey Sport is a great choice! Check out the following: No Accidents! One Owner! BLACK, LEATHER SEAT TRIM Safety and Security
  • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
  • Pedestrian impact prevention - An extra step toward safety. Pedestrians don't always stop, look, and listen, but with Pedestrian Impact Prevention, your vehicle is equipped to better see them and avoid them. This system constantly monitors the road ahead to identify and track pedestrians. It projects that image to an interior display screen, AND should an impact become likely, Pedestrian impact prevention takes steps to avoid a collision.
  • Rear camera - Watching your back! The rear camera helps you see obstacles and hazards you otherwise couldn't by showing enhanced images of what is behind you. The rear camera is an extra set of eyes that's both convenient and safe.
  • Lane departure prevention - Keep it between the lines. It only takes a moment of inattention for your vehicle to drift. With lane departure prevention, your vehicle takes corrective action to help you avoid unintentionally moving out of your lane. Lane departure prevention is an extra level of safety for you and those around you.
Technology and Telematics
  • Smart device mirroring - Smartphone, meet smart car. You can control your device through your vehicle's infotainment system. Smart device mirroring brings together safety and convenience by making it easier to find what you're looking for while keeping your eyes on the road.

Vehicle Details
Find exceptional value with this 2023 Chrysler Pacifica Touring L, located in Manchester, PA. This versatile minivan combines a smooth V6 3.6L gasoline engine with front-wheel drive for confident daily driving, highway cruising, and family road trips. The Touring L trim offers a thoughtful balance of comfort, convenience, and safety features designed to simplify every drive. Inside, the Chrysler Pacifica Touring L delivers a roomy, family-friendly cabin with flexible seating and cargo options to accommodate passengers and gear. Connectivity is seamless with both Apple CarPlay and Android Auto integration, keeping navigation, music, and messaging at your fingertips. Remote start adds convenience for cold mornings and warm afternoons, while advanced safety systems help protect what matters most. Standard safety features include Lane Departure Warning and Forward Collision Warning to assist the driver and enhance peace of mind on busy roads. This Chrysler Pacifica has been competitively priced to offer the best value in the Manchester, PA area—an excellent opportunity for buyers seeking a reliable, feature-rich minivan without compromise. Whether you need daily practicality or weekend versatility, the 2023 Chrysler Pacifica Touring L delivers performance, technology, and safety in one well-equipped package. Contact us to schedule a test drive and see why this Chrysler Pacifica represents the best price and outstanding value locally.

Equipment
This model offers Apple CarPlay for seamless connectivity. Start the Chrysler Pacifica from inside with remote start. This Chrysler Pacifica's Lane Departure Warning helps keep you in your lane. This unit's Forward Collision Warning system alerts the driver to potential front-end collisions, enhancing safety. Good News! This certified CARFAX 1-owner vehicle has only had one owner before you. It is pure luxury with a heated steering wheel. The leather seats in this mini van are a must for buyers looking for comfort, durability, and style. This model comes equipped with Android Auto for seamless smartphone integration on the road. This 2023 Chrysler Pacifica features a hands-free Bluetooth phone system. This unit keeps you comfortable with Auto Climate. This Chrysler Pacifica has automated speed control that adjusts to maintain a safe following distance, enhancing highway driving convenience. Protect this 2023 Chrysler Pacifica from unwanted accidents with a cutting edge backup camera system.

Packages

description:
LIFETIME WARRANTY LIFETIME WARRANTY LIFETIME WARRANTY LIFETIME WARRANTY
The 2023 Kia Carnival LX is a versatile and well-equipped minivan that offers exceptional value and a host of impressive features. With its striking red exterior, this Carnival LX is a standout on the road, turning heads wherever it goes.

• EC Mirror w/HomeLink
• Carpeted Floor Mats (8-Passenger)

The Carnival LX is powered by a robust V6 engine paired with an 8-speed automatic transmission, delivering an impressive balance of performance and efficiency. With an EPA-estimated 19 mpg in the city and 26 mpg on the highway, this minivan provides the perfect blend of power and fuel economy to meet your daily driving needs.

Beyond its exceptional powertrain, the Carnival LX is packed with a wealth of features that elevate the driving experience. Enjoy the convenience of Apple CarPlay and Android Auto, allowing you to seamlessly integrate your smartphone with the vehicle's infotainment system. Stay connected and entertained on the go with the 6-speaker audio system, while the rear air conditioning ensures your passengers remain comfortable.

The Carnival LX's spacious interior offers seating for up to 8 passengers, making it the perfect choice for growing families or those with active lifestyles. The split-folding third-row seat provides versatile cargo space, while the reclining third-row seat ensures your passengers can relax in comfort.

Safety is a top priority in the Carnival LX, with a host of advanced driver-assistance features to give you peace of mind on the road. Enjoy the added security of automatic high-beam headlights, a rear window wiper, and a security system, all of which work together to keep you and your loved ones protected.

Whether you're transporting the family, hauling gear, or simply enjoying the daily commute, the 2023 Kia Carnival LX is the perfect companion. With its impressive capabilities, thoughtful amenities, and striking good looks, this minivan is sure to exceed your expectations and provide an exceptional ownership experience.

We invite you to visit our showroom and experience the Carnival LX for yourself. Our knowledgeable sales team is here to answer any questions you may have and help you discover the perfect vehicle to meet your needs. Don't miss the opportunity to make the 2023 Kia Carnival LX your next automotive companion.

description:
Discover the perfect blend of style, comfort, and versatility with the 2023 Chrysler Pacifica Touring L. This exceptional minivan is the epitome of family-friendly transportation, offering a remarkable combination of advanced features and impressive performance.

Adorned in the sophisticated Granite Crystal Metallic Clearcoat, this Pacifica Touring L exudes a refined and modern aesthetic. Boasting a host of premium amenities, it's engineered to elevate your driving experience. Highlights include:

• Granite Crystal Metallic Clearcoat
• Quick Order Package 27L

The Pacifica Touring L is equipped with a powerful 3.6L V6 24V VVT engine, delivering a smooth and efficient ride with an impressive 19 city/28 highway MPG. Enjoy the convenience of the 9-Speed 948TE Automatic transmission and the confidence of Front-Wheel Drive.

Step inside and discover a world of comfort and convenience. The Integrated Active Noise Cancellation system ensures a serene cabin environment, while the Uconnect 5 infotainment system with a 10.1" display keeps you connected and entertained. Apple CarPlay, Android Auto, and a Caprice Leatherette Bucket Seats provide a premium experience.

Stay comfortable year-round with the Front Dual Zone Air Conditioning and Rear Air Conditioning. The Heated Steering Wheel and Heated Front Seats add a touch of luxury, while the Power Liftgate and ParkView Rear Back-Up Camera simplify your daily tasks.

Safety is a top priority in the Pacifica Touring L, with features like Front Fog Lights, Fully Automatic Headlights, and a suite of advanced airbags to keep you and your loved ones protected.

Elevate your family's transportation with the 2023 Chrysler Pacifica Touring L. Experience the perfect blend of style, comfort, and technology that will make every journey a pleasure. Visit our showroom today and discover how this exceptional minivan can enhance your life.

The Chrysler Voyager LX is a versatile and family friendly minivan designed for comfort, safety, and everyday convenience. Powered by a smooth 3.6L V6 engine paired with an automatic transmission, it delivers confident performance and a refined driving experience. This Voyager is equipped with a rear backup camera, push button start, power sliding doors, and a power liftgate for added ease when loading passengers or cargo. Inside, the cabin features heated front seats, a heated steering wheel, tri zone climate control, and flexible Stow n Go seating that allows the second and third rows to fold flat for impressive cargo space. Connectivity is seamless with Apple CarPlay, Android Auto, Bluetooth, steering wheel mounted controls, and a modern touchscreen display. With advanced safety features, smart interior design, and strong reliability, this Voyager LX is an excellent choice for families or anyone needing space and comfort in a dependable minivan.

description:
Discover the exceptional 2023 Chrysler Pacifica Touring L, a versatile and well-equipped family-friendly minivan that offers unparalleled comfort, convenience, and style. This stunning vehicle, finished in the sophisticated Granite Crystal Metallic Clearcoat, is a true standout on the road.

Boasting an impressive list of features, this Pacifica Touring L is the perfect companion for your adventures. Highlights include:

• 2 Keys!
• Accident Free Carfax!
• 1 Owner Vehicle!
• Granite Crystal Metallic Clearcoat
• Gray

Slip behind the wheel and experience the power of the 3.6L V6 24V VVT engine, paired with the smooth-shifting 9-Speed 948TE Automatic transmission, delivering a remarkable balance of performance and efficiency. With an EPA-estimated 19 MPG in the city and 28 MPG on the highway, this Pacifica will take you and your loved ones wherever you need to go, without sacrificing fuel economy.

The Pacifica Touring L is packed with an array of premium features that elevate your driving experience. Enjoy the convenience of the Power Liftgate, the comfort of Heated Front Seats, and the connectivity of the Uconnect 5 infotainment system with a stunning 10.1-inch touchscreen display. Stay connected with Apple CarPlay and Google Android Auto, while the ParkView Rear Back-Up Camera and Electronic Stability Control provide added peace of mind.

Designed with families in mind, the Pacifica offers ample seating for up to 8 passengers, with the versatility of a split-folding 3rd-row seat and Caprice Leatherette Bucket Seats. Whether you're embarking on a road trip or navigating the daily school run, this minivan has the space and features to accommodate your needs.

Experience the exceptional value and refined craftsmanship of the 2023 Chrysler Pacifica Touring L. With its impressive list of features, striking appearance, and exceptional performance, this vehicle is sure to exceed your expectations. Visit our showroom today and let us demonstrate why the Pacifica Touring L is the perfect choice for your next family vehicle.

description:
This 2023 Chrysler Pacifica Touring L is a family-friendly minivan that blends comfort, convenience, and versatility in every mile. With 70,224 miles, one owner, a no-accident history, and fully Certified status, this Pacifica is ready for daily driving, long road trips, and everything in between. Thoughtful design, smooth performance, and customer-favorite comfort features make it an excellent choice for families on the go.

Key Highlights

One Owner - Single-owner, well-maintained vehicle

Certified - Thorough inspection and certification completed

No Accidents - Clean history with no reported collisions

Spacious three-row seating and excellent cargo flexibility

Comfortable ride quality with modern technology

Performance & Capability

3.6L V6 Engine - Smooth, dependable power

Automatic Transmission

Front-Wheel Drive (FWD)

Engine Start/Stop Technology

Confident highway cruising and responsive handling

Interior Comfort & Convenience

This Pacifica Touring L offers a refined and family-friendly interior with customer-favorite features:

Seating for up to 7 passengers

Stow n Go Seating & Storage System - Fold seats into the floor for maximum cargo space

Heated Front Seats - Added comfort in colder weather

This 2023 Chrysler Pacifica Limited is a premium family-oriented minivan that stands out with a blend of comfort, capability, and modern features. The Pacifica's distinctive profile offers easy access with sliding rear doors, ample cabin space for up to seven or eight passengers, and a flexible interior that adapts to passengers easily --- ideal for daily school runs, road trips, or hauling gear. Built with a thoughtful balance of utility and refinement, the Pacifica Limited delivers a commanding yet composed presence on the road.

Under the hood, this Pacifica is powered by a 3.6L V6 engine paired with a smooth shifting 9-speed automatic transmission, providing responsive performance and effortless acceleration whether you're merging on the highway or navigating city streets. The front-wheel-drive setup complements the Pacifica's ride quality and fuel efficiency, making it a practical choice for families and daily drivers alike. Inside, the Limited trim typically brings higher-end amenities such as leather seating, advanced infotainment with Uconnect and navigation, adaptive cruise control, and integrated safety tech that enhance safety and convenience on every journey.

Comfort and convenience are core strengths of the Pacifica Limited, with features like power liftgate, heated seats, third-row seating, and extensive connectivity options helping to make every trip enjoyable for drivers and passengers alike. Its spacious interior and versatile seating configurations allow you to tailor the cabin to passengers or cargo needs, whether for everyday errands or longer excursions. With an appealing mix of performance, technology, and family-friendly design, this 2023 Chrysler Pacifica Limited represents a strong choice in the minivan segment.

Boasting a sleek white exterior, the Voyager LX commands attention on the road. Its thoughtfully designed interior features:

• Quick Order Package 27E
• Apple CarPlay and Google Android Auto
• Dual-zone automatic climate control
• Power driver's seat
• Heated front seats
• Power liftgate
• Rearview camera

The Voyager's 3.6L V6 engine and 9-speed automatic transmission deliver a smooth and efficient driving experience, with an impressive 28 MPG on the highway. Enjoy the confidence of responsive handling and the security of advanced safety features, including:

• Antilock brakes
• Stability and traction control
• Dual-stage airbags
• Rear parking sensors

Certified by our trusted technicians, this Voyager LX is ready to provide you and your family with years of reliable and enjoyable transportation. Experience the perfect balance of practicality and sophistication in this exceptional minivan.

Imagine the convenience of the Voyager's spacious interior, with seating for up to seven and ample cargo room. Whether you're embarking on a family road trip or tackling your daily errands, this Chrysler Voyager LX is the perfect companion.

Elevate your driving experience and discover the exceptional value of this 2023 Chrysler Voyager LX. Schedule a test drive today and see for yourself why this versatile minivan should be your next vehicle.

description:
This 2023 Chrysler Pacifica Limited is a premium minivan that combines family-focused versatility with upscale comfort and advanced technology, making it an excellent choice for drivers in Buffalo, MN and the surrounding area. Powered by Chrysler’s proven 3.6L V6 engine paired with a smooth 9-speed automatic transmission, the Pacifica delivers confident acceleration, refined ride quality, and impressive efficiency for daily commuting, road trips, and everything in between. As a Limited trim, it comes well equipped with desirable standard features such as leather-trimmed seating, tri-zone automatic climate control, a power-adjustable driver’s seat with memory, power passenger seat, remote start, and keyless entry with push-button start.
The interior is designed with both comfort and flexibility in mind. A large 10.1-inch touchscreen display with integrated navigation anchors the dash and provides seamless access to Apple CarPlay and Android Auto, 4G LTE Wi-Fi connectivity, wireless device charging, and a premium Alpine sound system. Heated and ventilated front seats, heated second-row seats, and a heated steering wheel ensure year-round comfort, while second- and third-row Stow ’n Go seating allows the cabin to quickly adapt from passenger duty to cargo hauling. Dual power sliding doors and a hands-free power liftgate add everyday convenience, and the panoramic sunroof fills the cabin with natural light.
This Pacifica Limited is a one-owner vehicle with a clean history, and a free CARFAX Vehicle History Report is available on our website for added confidence. As part of our commitment to quality at Ryan Chrysler Dodge Jeep Ram in Buffalo, this vehicle has completed our reconditioning process, including a multi-point inspection with oil change, new engine and cabin air filters, new front and rear wiper blades, and a complete exterior and interior detail.
Safety and driver-assist technology are a strong focus, with features that include adaptive cruise control, forward collision alert with pedestrian braking, lane departure warning, blind spot monitoring, rear cross path detection, rear park assist with automatic braking, a rear vision camera, fog lamps, and multiple airbags throughout the cabin. Additional highlights include deep tinted glass, a universal garage door opener, multiple-zone automatic climate control, and 18-inch painted silver Lithos aluminum wheels that complete the Pacifica’s refined appearance.
If you’re looking for a well-equipped, low-mileage minivan with premium features and family-friendly versatility near Buffalo, MN, this 2023 Chrysler Pacifica Limited is an excellent option. Contact us for availability and a test drive today. Buy with confidence at Ryan Auto Mall. With over 22,500 reviews, 9 GM Mark of Excellence awards, and 65 MN DealerRater Dealer of the Year honors, our reputation is proven. This pre-owned vehicle includes warranty coverage for added peace of mind. Pricing excludes tax, title, license, and a $350 doc fee. Every vehicle is pre-fitted with PULSE, our rear-end collision deterrent system, available for just $399. Visit us at 1000 E Highway 55, Buffalo, MN 55313, or call 763-373-9300 to schedule your test drive and experience the Ryan difference.

description:
Discover the exceptional 2023 Honda Odyssey EX-L, a sophisticated and versatile family-focused vehicle that seamlessly blends style, comfort, and advanced technology. With its sleek silver exterior and powerful 3.5L V6 engine paired with a smooth 10-speed automatic transmission, this Odyssey is ready to elevate your driving experience.

• Memory seat
• Power moonroof
• Power Liftgate
• Blind Spot Information (BSI) System warning
• Lane Keeping Assist System (LKAS) active
• Apple CarPlay/Android Auto
• Heated front seats
• Leather Seat Trim
• Power passenger seat

This well-equipped Odyssey EX-L offers an array of premium features that cater to your every need. Enjoy the convenience of a power liftgate, the safety of Blind Spot Information (BSI) System, and the seamless connectivity of Apple CarPlay and Android Auto. The leather-trimmed interior and heated front seats provide a luxurious and comfortable driving experience, while the memory seat function ensures your perfect seating position is always within reach.

Designed with your family's well-being in mind, the Odyssey boasts a spacious and versatile cabin, offering ample room for up to eight passengers. The split-folding third-row seat and the 60/40 split-folding second-row seat provide unparalleled flexibility, allowing you to customize the interior to accommodate your ever-changing needs. Whether you're transporting the kids to their activities, taking a road trip with friends, or embarking on a weekend getaway, the Odyssey is ready to handle it all with ease.

Efficiency and performance go hand in hand with this Odyssey. The 3.5L V6 engine delivers a satisfying 19 city/28 highway mpg, ensuring you can enjoy the open road without frequent stops at the pump. The 10-speed automatic transmission provides seamless and responsive power delivery, making every drive a pleasure.

Safety is a top priority in the Odyssey, with features like the Lane Keeping Assist System (LKAS) and the Blind Spot Information (BSI) System keeping you and your loved ones secure on the road. The Adaptive Cruise Control with Low-Speed Follow function adds an extra layer of confidence, allowing you to navigate traffic with ease.

Experience the exceptional quality and versatility of the 2023 Honda Odyssey EX-L. This remarkable vehicle is ready to elevate your family's adventures and provide the ultimate in comfort, convenience, and peace of mind. Visit our showroom today to take this impressive Odyssey for a test drive and discover why it's the perfect choice for your next chapter.

All qualifying pre-owned vehicle's come with our drive forever limited lifetime powertrain warranty, exclusions apply see sales associate for details.

Safety and Security
  • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
  • Forward collision mitigation - Forward thinking. You look away for just a second and suddenly the vehicle in front of you has stopped. That's when the forward collision mitigation system comes to life. When it senses an impending impact, it will activate a combination of features to help prevent or reduce the severity of an accident. Forward collision mitigation is always looking ahead.
  • Pedestrian impact prevention - An extra step toward safety. Pedestrians don't always stop, look, and listen, but with Pedestrian Impact Prevention, your vehicle is equipped to better see them and avoid them. This system constantly monitors the road ahead to identify and track pedestrians. It projects that image to an interior display screen, AND should an impact become likely, Pedestrian impact prevention takes steps to avoid a collision.
Technology and Telematics
  • Smart device mirroring - Smartphone, meet smart car. You can control your device through your vehicle's infotainment system. Smart device mirroring brings together safety and convenience by making it easier to find what you're looking for while keeping your eyes on the road.
  • Apple CarPlay/Android Auto smart device wireless mirroring

description:
Experience the pinnacle of family-friendly luxury with this exceptional 2022 Honda Odyssey EX-L. This captivating minivan seamlessly blends advanced technology, unparalleled comfort, and exceptional versatility, making it the ultimate choice for discerning buyers seeking the ultimate in modern family transportation.

Boasting an impressive array of premium features, this Odyssey EX-L is equipped to elevate your driving experience. Key highlights include:

• 7 Speakers
• AM/FM radio: SiriusXM
• Radio data system
• Radio: 160-Watt AM/FM/HD/SiriusXM Audio System
• Automatic temperature control
• Rear air conditioning
• Power driver seat
• Power moonroof
• Power Liftgate
• Blind Spot Information (BSI) System warning
• Collision Mitigation Braking System (CMBS) + FCW mitigation
• Lane Keeping Assist System (LKAS) active
• Adaptive Cruise Control (ACC) with Low-Speed Follow
• Apple CarPlay/Android Auto

Beneath the striking Platinum White Pearl exterior lies a powerful 3.5L V6 engine, delivering an exceptional blend of performance and efficiency, with an EPA-estimated 19 city/28 highway MPG. The 10-speed automatic transmission ensures seamless power delivery, while the front-wheel-drive system provides confident handling in all driving conditions.

Slip behind the wheel of this meticulously maintained Odyssey, and you'll be greeted by a spacious and luxuriously appointed cabin. The EX-L trim level elevates the experience with heated front seats, a power-adjustable driver's seat, and a leather-wrapped steering wheel, creating an environment of unparalleled comfort and sophistication.

Versatility is the hallmark of the Odyssey, with a split-folding third-row seat and ample cargo space that easily accommodate your family's needs. Whether you're transporting the kids to soccer practice, embarking on a road trip, or simply running daily errands, this Honda minivan is the perfect companion.

Safety is paramount in the Odyssey, with a comprehensive suite of advanced driver-assistance technologies, including Collision Mitigation Braking System, Lane Keeping Assist, and Adaptive Cruise Control, providing you with the confidence to navigate the roads with peace of mind.

Discover the perfect blend of style, performance, and functionality with this exceptional 2022 Honda Odyssey EX-L. Schedule a test drive today and experience the ultimate in family-focused transportation.

description:
Experience premium family adventures in this exceptional 2022 Chrysler Pacifica Touring L with only 43,564 low miles! This luxury minivan delivers unmatched comfort and cutting-edge technology.

Safety Excellence: Earned a prestigious 5-Star Overall Safety Rating with advanced protection including Blind Spot Detection, Forward Collision Warning-Plus, Lane Departure Warning-Plus, and Pedestrian Impact Prevention. Park Assist automatic vehicle parking and ParkView rear mounted camera make every maneuver effortless.

Luxury & Convenience: Heated leather front seats with 8-way driver adjustments, heated steering wheel, and power liftgate rear cargo door elevate every journey. Stay connected with wireless Apple CarPlay/Android Auto and 11 USB ports throughout the cabin. Keyless Enter 'n Go with push button start and keyfob remote start add premium convenience.

Smart Flexibility: Manual fold-into-floor second-row seats maximize cargo space, while adaptive cruise control with stop and go enhances highway comfort. The efficient 3.6L V-6 engine delivers 287HP with cylinder deactivation technology.

Low Mileage Advantage: At just 43,564 miles, this Pacifica offers years of reliable family adventures ahead.

Butler Nissan Promise: Located at 4500 Riverside Dr in Macon, we're committed to transparent pricing and exceptional service to help you find your perfect family vehicle.

description:
Discover the Chrysler Pacifica Touring L - the epitome of family-friendly sophistication. This 2022 model boasts an impressive array of features that seamlessly blend style, comfort, and convenience.

• Heated seats and steering wheel for cozy drives
• Memory seat for personalized comfort
• Push-button start and remote keyless entry for effortless access
• Hands-free Bluetooth and Apple CarPlay/Android Auto for seamless connectivity
• Powerful 3.6L V6 engine with 9-speed automatic transmission for responsive performance
• Rear backup camera and advanced safety technologies like automatic emergency braking for added peace of mind

The Pacifica Touring L's sleek Granite Crystal Metallic exterior and spacious, well-appointed interior make it the perfect choice for families who demand both style and substance. With seating for up to 8 and ample cargo space, this minivan offers the versatility to accommodate your growing needs.

description: Make family travel the best part of your day with this 2022 Chrysler Voyager LX. Finished in a clean Bright White Clearcoat, this minivan is the ultimate "value-plus" family hauler. As a CARFAX One-Owner with a clean CARFAX, this Voyager offers a history as spotless as its exterior, providing you with a reliable, modern vehicle that is ready to tackle everything from the morning carpool to your next cross-country vacation.Under the hood, the Voyager is powered by the award-winning 3.6L V6 Pentastar engine, delivering 287 horsepower for confident highway merging and smooth passing power. Paired with a 9-speed automatic transmission and a specialized Touring Suspension, it provides a quiet and composed ride that rivals much more expensive luxury vans. Plus, with an impressive 19/28 City/Highway MPG, you can spend more time making memories and less time at the pump.The real magic happens inside the cabin, where you'll find Chrysler's industry-exclusive Stow 'n Go seating. Both the second and third rows can fold completely flat into the floor in seconds, transforming your seven-passenger shuttle into a massive cargo hauler with 140 cubic feet of space. The Quick Order Package 27E adds even more convenience, including a Power Liftgate and power-sliding side doors, making it effortless to load groceries or help the kids out of the car.Comfort is front and center with standard heated front seats and a heated steering wheel, ensuring you stay cozy even on the coldest Arkansas mornings. The triple-zone automatic climate control allows everyone to choose their own perfect temperature, while the Uconnect 5 system with a 7-inch touchscreen keeps you connected. With wireless Apple CarPlay and Android Auto, you can access your maps, messages, and music without ever having to plug in your phone.At the Superior Pre-Owned Superstore of Bentonville, we make it our mission to provide a car-buying experience that is faster, simpler, and more transparent. This Voyager has been professionally cleaned and serviced to ensure it feels like a brand-new van the moment you drive away. Let us show you what your trade is worth and help you get the keys to a vehicle your family truly deserves. Visit us at http://www.bentonvillepreowned.com or call today!Faster. Simpler. More Transparent. Superior Automotive Group has helped thousands of customers find the right car by leveraging one of Arkansas' largest selections of new and pre-owned vehicles at unparalleled prices. Yet, it's our extra-mile customer service and uncommonly candid and respectful staff that have won the trust and loyalty of Arkansas drivers for 30 years. Come visit one of our Superior dealerships today and let us exceed your expectations.

Discover excellent value with this 2022 Chrysler Voyager LX, now available in Hopkinsville, KY. Equipped with a smooth and capable 3.6L V6 gasoline engine and front-wheel drive, this Chrysler Voyager delivers dependable performance, comfortable highway cruising, and confident acceleration for families and daily commuters alike. The LX trim includes driver-focused conveniences such as Remote Start for easy climate control on chilly mornings and a Heated Steering Wheel to keep hands warm during winter drives.

Discover space, comfort, and confidence in the 2022 Chrysler Pacifica Touring L — a standout choice in the minivan segment that perfectly blends family-friendly versatility with upscale features. - Rear backup camera

Reliable, spacious, and loaded with features, the 2022 Chrysler Pacifica Touring L delivers everything your family needs — comfort, versatility, and confidence in every mile.

description:
Discover the exceptional 2020 Hyundai Ioniq Electric SE, a testament to the future of sustainable mobility. This all-electric marvel boasts an impressive 145 MPGe in the city and 121 MPGe on the highway, ensuring you can conquer your daily commute with confidence and efficiency.

• MARYLAND STATE INSPECTED

Under the hood, the Ioniq Electric's advanced electric motor and single-speed transmission deliver smooth, responsive performance, seamlessly translating your driving inputs into effortless acceleration and precise control. Coupled with the vehicle's front-wheel-drive configuration, you'll experience a dynamic and engaging driving experience that redefines the electric car segment.

The Ioniq Electric SE's sleek, modern exterior is complemented by a host of premium features, including:
• 6 Speakers
• AM/FM radio: SiriusXM
• Radio: AM/FM Display Audio
• Air Conditioning
• Automatic temperature control
• Rear window defroster
• Power steering
• Power windows
• Remote keyless entry
• Steering wheel mounted audio controls
• Speed-sensing steering
• Traction control

Step inside the Ioniq Electric SE and you'll be greeted by a well-appointed cabin that prioritizes your comfort and convenience. Heated front seats, a premium cloth upholstery, and a host of advanced technology features, such as Apple CarPlay and Android Auto, ensure a truly exceptional driving experience.

Safety is also a top priority, with the Ioniq Electric SE featuring a comprehensive suite of advanced driver-assistance technologies, including:
• 4-Wheel Disc Brakes
• ABS brakes
• Dual front impact airbags
• Dual front side impact airbags
• Emergency communication system: Blue Link Connected Care (3-year subscription)
• Front anti-roll bar
• Front wheel independent suspension
• Knee airbag
• Low tire pressure warning
• Occupant sensing airbag
• Overhead airbag
• Brake assist
• Electronic Stability Control

• Auto High-beam Headlights
• Delay-off headlights
• Fully automatic headlights
• Panic alarm
• Security system

With a sleek, modern design, impressive efficiency, and a wealth of premium features, the 2020 Hyundai Ioniq Electric SE is a truly exceptional value proposition. Experience the future of electric mobility today with this remarkable vehicle, priced at just $12,500. Visit our showroom to take this Ioniq for a test drive and discover the difference for yourself.

description:
Vehicle Details
Discover exceptional value with this certified pre-owned 2024 Chrysler Pacifica Touring L, now available in Valparaiso, IN. With only 47,935 miles and a responsive 3.6L V6 gasoline engine paired to efficient FWD, this Chrysler Pacifica blends power, comfort, and reliability for family drives and daily commutes. Priced to sell, it offers the best price in the area for a certified model, giving you peace of mind with inspected quality and added warranty coverage.

Inside, premium leather seats provide lasting comfort for driver and passengers, while practical features enhance every trip. Adaptive Cruise Control and Forward Collision Warning add an advanced safety layer for highway confidence, helping maintain distance and alerting you to potential hazards. A heated steering wheel keeps hands warm on chilly mornings, and remote start lets you pre-condition the cabin for immediate comfort.

The Touring L trim balances upscale amenities with smart functionality, offering roomy seating and flexible cargo options for weekend getaways or carpool routes. This certified Chrysler Pacifica has been through a rigorous inspection and meets strict manufacturer standards, making it a smart buy for families seeking safety, reliability, and value.

Located in Valparaiso, IN, this 2024 Chrysler Pacifica Touring L at the best price won't last long. Contact us today to schedule a test drive and experience this versatile minivan for yourself.

Equipment
This 2024 Chrysler Pacifica has auto-adjust speed for safe following. This model offers Android Auto for seamless smartphone integration. Apple CarPlay: Seamless smartphone integration for this mini van - stay connected and entertained on the go! This unit offers Automatic Climate Control for personalized comfort. This vehicle has an automatic transmission. Protect this model from unwanted accidents with a cutting edge backup camera system. Good News! This certified CARFAX 1-owner vehicle has only had one owner before you. Our dealership has already run the CARFAX report and it is clean. A clean CARFAX is a great asset for resale value in the future. This vehicle is a manufacturer certified pre-owned vehicle. Set the temperature exactly where you are most comfortable in this mini van. The fan speed and temperature will automatically adjust to maintain your preferred zone climate. It features cruise control for long trips. Electronic Stability Control is one of many advanced safety features on this vehicle. This unit has a V6, 3.6L high output engine. The fog lights cut through the weather so you can see what's ahead. The vehicle's Forward Collision Warning feature alerts drivers to potential front-end collisions. Front wheel drive on the Chrysler Pacifica gives you better traction and better fuel economy. Enjoy the tried and true gasoline engine in the Chrysler Pacifica. This 2024 Chrysler Pacifica features a hands-free Bluetooth phone system. Keep your hands warm all winter with a heated steering wheel in the vehicle . Quickly unlock the vehicle with keyless entry. This vehicle's Lane Departure Warning helps keep you in your lane. The leather seats in this mini van are a must for buyers looking for comfort, durability, and style. Help alleviate lower back pain with the driver seat lumbar support in this model. Get the whole family to events in this minivan. Enjoy the convenience of the power liftgate on this model. The rear parking assist technology on it will put you at ease when reversing. The system alerts you as you get closer to an obstruction. Start the Chrysler Pacifica from inside with remote start. This mini van gleams with an elegant silver clear coated finish.

Packages
Quick Order Package 27L Silver Mist Clearcoat **Equipment listed is based on original vehicle build and subject to change. Please confirm the accuracy of the included equipment by calling the dealer prior to purchase.**

Additional Information
Grieger's Motor Sales - Family Owned & Community Focused. *Prices include rebates for Great Lakes Business Center residents as defined by FCA US LLC. Some savings require financing with Stellantis Financial Services. Residency restrictions may apply. Select rebates may be in lieu of special financing offers. Contact dealer to verify your residency is within Business Center. Plus tax, title & $235 documentation. Vehicles subject to prior sale. No sales to dealers, brokers or anyone who buys for the sole purpose of resale or export sales.

Step into the sophisticated world of the 2024 Chrysler Pacifica Touring L. This captivating minivan is a true masterpiece of engineering, blending style, comfort, and cutting-edge technology to elevate your driving experience.

Highlighted by a sleek black exterior, the Pacifica Touring L commands attention wherever it goes. Under the hood, a powerful 3.6L V6 24V VVT engine, paired with a responsive 9-Speed 948TE Automatic transmission, delivers an exceptional balance of power and efficiency, with an impressive 19 city and 28 highway MPG.

• Quick Order Package 27L
• Uconnect 5 with 10.1" Touchscreen Display
• Apple CarPlay and Android Auto
• Caprice Leatherette Bucket Seats
• Heated Steering Wheel
• Power Liftgate

This meticulously maintained Pacifica Touring L is equipped with a wealth of premium features that elevate the driving experience. From the advanced Uconnect 5 infotainment system with a stunning 10.1-inch touchscreen display to the convenient power liftgate, every detail has been thoughtfully designed to make your life easier.

Slip into the comfort of the Caprice Leatherette Bucket Seats and enjoy the warmth of the heated steering wheel, creating a cozy and inviting atmosphere. The Pacifica's impressive 42,736-mile odometer speaks to its well-cared-for condition, ensuring you can confidently take the wheel and embark on your next adventure.

Versatility is the hallmark of the Pacifica Touring L, with a split-folding third-row seat and ample cargo space to accommodate all your needs. Whether you're transporting the family, hauling gear, or simply enjoying the open road, this minivan is up to the task.

Safety is paramount, and the Pacifica Touring L delivers with a suite of advanced driver-assistance technologies, including ParkView Rear Back-Up Camera, Brake Assist, and Electronic Stability Control, providing you with the confidence to navigate the roads with ease.

Experience the ultimate in family-friendly transportation with the 2024 Chrysler Pacifica Touring L. Schedule a test drive today and discover why this exceptional minivan is the perfect choice for your lifestyle.

description:
Family Road-Trip Hero: 2024 Chrysler Pacifica Hybrid Select Drive your Dreams

When your family calendar is packed, and your fuel budget is not, this 2024 Chrysler Pacifica Hybrid Select is exactly the kind of smart, comfortable ride you want in your driveway. At Tom Tepe Autocenter in Milan, Indiana, and Car Country in Aurora, IN, and Harrison, OH, we serve families all over Milan, Aurora, Harrison, Greater Cincinnati, and Northern Kentucky who need space, efficiency, and everyday convenience in one good-looking minivan.

This Carfax One-Owner Pacifica Hybrid Select in Silver Mist Clearcoat wraps advanced tech and a hybrid powertrain around a genuinely relaxing interior. The 3.6L V6 Hybrid, matched to a smooth CVT, helps you sip fuel on school runs, commutes, and weekend trips, while still having the power you need when the van is full of people, gear, and groceries.

Inside, everyone gets a comfortable spot. Caprice leatherette bucket seats, heated front seats, and a heated steering wheel make cold Indiana and Ohio mornings much easier to face. The 3rd-row split-bench with reclining function and rear air conditioning means kids, teens, and friends stay comfortable all the way to the ballfield, the mall, or downtown Cincinnati.

Up front, your drive stays connected and in control. The Uconnect 5 system with 10.1" touchscreen, Apple CarPlay, and Android Auto brings your maps, music, and messages to life with an easy, tablet-like interface. Navigation helps you avoid wrong turns on new routes, and steering wheel-mounted audio controls keep your eyes where they belong on the road.

Daily life feels simpler thanks to a power liftgate, power driver seat with memory, and remote keyless entry. Sliding in and out of tight parking lots, school pick-up lines, and church parking is easier with the exterior parking camera, heated mirrors, and rain-sensing wipers that automatically adjust when the weather turns.

Safety is built right in. You get Electronic Stability Control, multiple airbags (including knee and side-impact), an emergency communication system, and four-wheel disc brakes with ABS working together to help protect what matters most in your world, your people.

If you're ready for a minivan that makes every errand, road trip, and carpool smoother and more efficient, this 2024 Chrysler Pacifica Hybrid Select deserves a test drive. Explore more photos, payment options, and our full inventory at https://www.TomTepe.com/and let Tom Tepe Autocenter and Car Country help you Drive your Dreams across Southeast Indiana and the Cincinnati Metro area.

Key Equipment Highlights (No More Than Eight):

3.6L V6 Hybrid powertrain with CVT

Caprice leatherette bucket seats with heated front seats & heated steering wheel

Uconnect 5 Nav with 10.1" display, Apple CarPlay & Android Auto

3rd-row split-bench seat with rear air conditioning

Exterior parking camera rear & Electronic Stability Control

Power liftgate, power driver seat with memory, power windows & locks

Rain-sensing wipers, front fog lights, heated power mirrors

17" x 7.0" diamond cut wheels with painted pockets

description:
Family-Hauling Hero Drive your Dreams in this 2024 Chrysler Pacifica Hybrid Select

At Tom Tepe Autocenter in Milan, Indiana, and Car Country in Aurora, IN, and Harrison, OH, we know families around Southeast Indiana, Greater Cincinnati, and Northern Kentucky need a vehicle that can juggle school runs, weekend ballgames, and road trips without feeling like a compromise. This Carfax One-Owner 2024 Chrysler Pacifica Hybrid Select in Brilliant Black Crystal Pearlcoat is exactly that kind of smart, stylish people-mover.

Under the hood, the 3.6L V6 hybrid powertrain teams up with a smooth CVT to give you confident acceleration plus impressive efficiency. Paired with four-wheel independent suspension and heavy-duty suspension, the Pacifica Hybrid feels composed on I-275, smooth on rural Indiana backroads, and easy to maneuver in tight parking lots around Milan, Aurora, Harrison, and the Cincinnati Metro area.

Inside, it's all about comfort and flexibility. Caprice leatherette bucket seats and a reclining third-row split-bench mean everyone from front-row drivers to third-row teens gets real support and space. Automatic temperature control, rear air conditioning, and heated front seats with a heated steering wheel keep the cabin comfortable in every season, from frosty Indiana mornings to hot Ohio afternoons.

Technology keeps your crew connected and happy. The Uconnect 5 Nav system with a 10.1" display, Apple CarPlay/Android Auto, and 6-speaker audio makes it easy to stream playlists, follow navigation, and take hands-free calls. Integrated active noise cancellation helps keep the cabin quiet, so conversations and podcasts don't have to compete with road noise.

Safety is built in, not bolted on. You get Electronic Stability Control, a full suite of airbags including knee and side-impact, rain-sensing wipers, an exterior parking camera, and an emergency communication system for added peace of mind. Heated power mirrors with turn-signal indicators boost visibility on busy Cincinnati and Northern Kentucky highways, while 4-wheel disc ABS brakes help you stop with confidence when traffic suddenly slows.

Whether you're browsing new vehicles at Tom Tepe Autocenter in Milan or shopping quality pre-owned options at Car Country in Aurora and Harrison, this Pacifica Hybrid Select reflects our commitment to at-or-under-market pricing and ASE-certified reconditioning for families all across our region.

Ready to see how easily this van can plug into your busy life? Explore photos, pricing, payment options, and more great family-focused content anytime at https://www.TomTepe.com/and let us help you Drive your Dreams.

Key Equipment Highlights (No More Than Eight):

3.6L V6 hybrid powertrain with CVT

Apple CarPlay/Android Auto with Uconnect 5 Nav 10.1" display

Caprice leatherette bucket seats with heated front seats

Heated steering wheel & heated power mirrors with signals

3rd-row split-bench with reclining seatbacks

Power liftgate & remote keyless entry

Rain-sensing wipers, 4-wheel disc ABS brakes, Electronic Stability Control

Integrated active noise cancellation & rear air conditioning

#DriveYourDreams #PacificaHybrid #FamilyVan #TomTepeAutocenter #CarCountry #MilanIndiana #AuroraIndiana #HarrisonOhio #CincinnatiDrivers #NorthernKentuckyFamilies

2024 Chrysler Voyager LX – Diamond Black Crystal Pearlcoat – Family Passenger Van

This 2024 Chrysler Voyager LX is a practical and family-friendly passenger van finished in Diamond Black Crystal Pearlcoat with Black cloth seating.
